quran[842]{c,v,t}:
  37,1,Ndarahiye kubatonze imirongo n’iyindi
  37,2,Kandi kuri barya batuza amabi yose
  37,3,Kandi kuri barya basoma ubutumwa bw’Imana
  37,4,Mu vy’ukuri Imana yanyu niyo yonyene gusa
  37,5,"Umuremyi\tw’Amajuru\tn’Isi\thamwe\tnibimwo\thagati\tyavyo\tkandi n’Umuremyi w’ubuseruko bwose"
  37,6,Ntankeka twebwe twarasharije Ijuru riri hafi kw’isharizo ry’Inyenyeri
  37,7,Nukuyi kingira n’amashetani yataye umurongo
  37,8,"Ntibashobore\tkwumviriza\tibiremwa\tvyeranda\tno\tmugihe\tbirukanywe kumpande zose"
  37,9,"Bazoshirwa kure, kandi bazoba bafise n’ibihano bitazoba vako"
  37,10,"Dukuye\tmwo\tuwusahuye\tikintu\tgitoyi\tmunyuma\tagaca\takurikiranwa n’igishirira gisayangana"
  37,11,"Nimubabaze muti:- mbega nibo bafise ishusho rikomeye cane canke barya twaremye, ntankeka ni twebwe twabaremye tubakuye mw’ivu rimatanye n’irindi"
  37,12,Mbega uratangara nabo babifata minenerwe
  37,13,Mugihe batujijwe ntiba gondozwa
  37,14,Mugihe babonye ibitangaro vyacu babifata minenerwe
  37,15,"Nukuvuga\tbati:-\tntivyari\tkuba\tibi\tvyose\tatari\tuko\tari\tuburozi\tburi k’umugaragaro"
  37,16,Mbega mugihe tuzosandaba nukuba ivu n’amagufa niko kuzoba ari ukuri kukuzurwa
  37,17,N’abatama bacu bakera
  37,18,"Vuga uti:- egome muri ico gihe muzoba muri mubihano bitazoba vako"
  37,19,Iyo mumuriro udahera hazoba hari induru yurutavana ko munyuma yaho bazobona umuhero w’Isi washitse
  37,20,"Bazovuga bati:- yo! Uwu niwo wamusi w’impembo"
  37,21,Uwu niwo musi wugucibwa urubanza mwahora muhakana
  37,22,Begeranye bamwe bahemukiye imitima yabo hamwe n’abagenzi babo hamwe nabo bahora basenga
  37,23,"Aho\tgusenga\tImana\tnimuba\trongore\tmunzira\tyomu\tmuriro\tudahera witiriwe Jahannamu"
  37,24,Nimuba hagarike mu vy’ukuri bazobazwa
  37,25,Mufise iki ko mutarokorana
  37,26,Kuri uwo musi bazoteterwa bimwe bitarabaho
  37,27,Bazokwinjira babazanya bamwe n’abandi
  37,28,"Bavuga\tbati:-\tmu\tvy’ukuri\tmwebwe\tmwamye\tmudushikira\tmunzira z’ukuri"
  37,29,"Nabo bishure bati:- ahubwo mwebwe bonyene ntimwari muba Isilamu"
  37,30,Ntabubasha twari dufise hejuru yanyu mugabo mwebwe nyene mwari mubataye umurongo w’ukuri
  37,31,Rero intahe y’Umuremyi wacu iramaze gucibwa ntankeka tuzoyihonja
  37,32,Nitwebwe bonyene twabatakaje tukaba twari mubantu bazimiye
  37,33,Rero mu vy’ukuri kuri uwo musi bazoba bari mubihano bakoranijwe hamwe
  37,34,Uku niko tuzogira abo bataye umurongo
  37,35,"Mugihe\tbahora\tbabwirwa\tyuko\tatayindi\tMana\titegerezwa\tgusengwa bimwe vy’ukuri atari Imana y’ukuri baguma banana"
  37,36,"Nukuvuga bati:- yo! twebwe dusige Imana zacu kubera uyo ategura amajambo y’ubuhizi nawe ari umusazi"
  37,37,"Ahubwo\tyaje\tafise\tukuri\tnukwemeza\tintumwa\tz’Imana\tzose\tzabaye imbere yiwe"
  37,38,Mu vy’ukuri mwebwe ntankeka muzohonja ibihano bibabaza cane
  37,39,Kandi ntimuzohembwa atari kuvyo mwahora mugira
  37,40,Dukuyemwo abantu beranda b’Imana bagize ibikorwa vyabo vyiza
  37,41,Abo bantu nibo bazoronka imigisha yabo bwite
  37,42,Ivyamwa vy’ubwoko bwose kandi baterwe n’iteka ntangere
  37,43,Mumirima y’imigisha myiza
  37,44,Bari hejuru y’ubusaswa barabana n’abandi amaso kuyandi
  37,45,Bakikuzwa n’ibirahuri birimwo ibinyobwa vyiza cane
  37,46,Vyera derere bifise n’akanovera kuri abo bantu babinywera mwo
  37,47,"Kuri\tivyo\tbinywobwa\tntangorane\tn’imwe\tzizoba\tzirimwo\tcanke ugutakaza ubwenge"
  37,48,Bazoba bari kumwe n’abapfasoni bafise amaso meza manini maniniya
  37,49,Abo bapfasoni bameze nk’amagi yabitswe neza
  37,50,Bazohura bamwe n’abandi babazanya
  37,51,"Hanyuma avuge umuvugizi umwe muribo ati:- mu vy’ukuri jewe nari mfise umugenzi"
  37,52,"Uwahora ambwira ati:- mbega wewe uri muri bamwe bemera\tImana yabo y’ukuri"
  37,53,"Yuko\tmugihe\ttwebwe\ttuzo\tsandaba\tnukuba\tivu\tn’amagufa\tmbega twebwe tuzorihwa"
  37,54,"Nawe azovuga ati:- mbega muzo mu runguruka"
  37,55,Nawe azo runguruka aze amubone ari hagati y’umuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu
  37,56,"Hanyuma aze amubwire ati:- ndarahiye kw’izina ry’Imana wewe wari wegereje kunzimiza"
  37,57,"Iyo\titaba\timigisha\ty’Umuremyi\twanje\tntankeka\tnari\tkuba\tmubo shengezwa n’ibihano vyo mumuriro udahera"
  37,58,Mbega na twebwe turi mu bantu bazo subira kwitaba Umuremyi wacu
  37,59,"Atari\turupfu\trwacu\trwaho\thambere\tkandi\ttwebwe\tntituzo\tsubira guhanwa"
  37,60,Ntankeka iyi niyo ntsinzi niniya
  37,61,Rero akarorero nkaka niko bogira abo bogira
  37,62,"Mbega ikaze nkiri siryiza, canke kuronka igiti citiriwe Zaqqum"
  37,63,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twagize ico giti nk’igihano caba hemukiye imitima yabo
  37,64,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tico\tn’igiti\tkivuye\thagati\ty’umuriro\tudahera\twitiriwe Jahannamu"
  37,65,Ivyamwa vy’ico giti bimeze nk’imitwe y’amashetani
  37,66,Ntankeka bazofungura kuri ico giti no kurico buzuze inda zabo
  37,67,Hanyuma ntankeka bazo shikirwa kubera uburure bw’ico giti n’uruvange rw’amazi y’amarike
  37,68,Hanyuma mu vy’ukuri ingaruka yabo bantu yazoba ari ayo mumuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu
  37,69,Mu vy’ukuri basanze abavyeyi babo barazimiye
  37,70,Nabo nyene baca batwarwa nugukurikira ingendo zabo
  37,71,Kandi ntankeka abantu benshi bakera barazimiye imbere yabo
  37,72,Mu vy’ukuri twararungitse abagabisha kuri abo bantu
  37,73,Rero nurabe uko yabaye amaherezo yabo bantu batujijwe
  37,74,Atari abagamburutsi b’Imana bigiriye ibikorwa vyabo vyiza
  37,75,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tintumwa\ty’Imana\tNuhu\t(iii)\tyaraduteye\takamo, n’abamwitavye b’intungane tumeze gute twebwe"
  37,76,Twaramurokoye hamwe n’abantu biwe bari muvyago bihambaye
  37,77,Twarahezagiye umuryango wiwe ngo babe aribo baguma kw’Isi
  37,78,Duca tumusigira ku bantu baje munyuma yiwe
  37,79,Amahoro y’intumwa y’Imana Nuhu (iii) asasagare kw’Isi yose
  37,80,Mu vy’ukuri uku niko duhemba abagira ineza
  37,81,Mu vy’ukuri yari mubantu bacu bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  37,82,Munyuma yaho niho twaca twibiza bamwe n’abandi
  37,83,Mu vy’ukuri intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (III) yari mumurwi wiwe
  37,84,Yarayikoreye idini y’Umuremyi wiwe n’umutima mwiza cane
  37,85,"Yaramubwiye\tSe\twiwe\thamwe\tn’abantu\tbiwe\tati:-\tmbega\tmwebwe musenga iki"
  37,86,"Kuvyiyadukije gusa vy’amamana aho yobaye Imana y’ukuri, nizo Mana mwipfuza"
  37,87,None n’ibihe vyiyumviro vyanyu hejuru y’Umuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose
  37,88,Hanyuma yaciye yitegereza mu kwitegereza kunyenyeri
  37,89,"Avuga ati:- mu vy’ukuri jewe ndarwaye"
  37,90,Nabo baramuretse gutyo baca bamuha ibitugu barigira
  37,91,"Nawe aca agenda mumpisho no ku Mana zabo azibwira ati:- mbega mufise iki ko muda fungura"
  37,92,Mubaye gute ko mutavuga
  37,93,Hanyuma arahindukira abakubita n’ukuboko kwiwe kw’iburyo
  37,94,Baca baza n’ingoga na ningoga
  37,95,"Aca ababwira ati:- oh! Mbega musenga muvyo mwibaziye kubwanyu n’amaboko yanyu"
  37,96,Mugihe Imana ariyo yabaremwye hamwe nivyo mugira vyose
  37,97,"Nabo\tbishura\tbati:-\tnimu\tmwubakire\tinyubakwa\thanyuma\tmu mujugunyire muri uwo mukomezwa"
  37,98,"Rero bashatse kumu girira amarorerwa, mugabo duca\ttuba girira kuba aribo badebukiwe"
  37,99,"Nayo intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii) yababwiye iti:- jewe ndagiye ku Muremyi wanje niwe azondongora"
  37,100,"Ewe Muremyi wanje, numpe mu bantu bagira ineza"
  37,101,Niho twamuha inkuru nziza y’ikibondo gitekanye
  37,102,"Mugihe yashika kurugero rw’ukugenda nukugaruka ari kumwe nawe niho yamubwira ati:- ewe kibondo canje, mu vy’ukuri jewe nabonye mundoto zanje yuko no kubaga, rero nawe niwiyumvire neza, none wewe ubibona gute? Nawe amwishura ati:- ewe data wanje nugire nk’uko wategetswe nanje uzonsanga Imana ibishatse ndimu bantu batenyenya"
  37,103,Bose hamwe uko ari babiri mugihe biyemeza imbere y’Imana nuguca amuryamika hasi kugira ngo amubage
  37,104,"Muri uwo mwanya isase twaciye tumu hamagara duti:- ewe ntumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii)"
  37,105,"Uramaze kwemeza yandoto yawe, mu vy’ukuri uku rero niko duhemba abagira neza bose"
  37,106,Ntankeka iri n’igeragezo riri k’umugaragaro
  37,107,Rero duca dukabisha n’igikoko cukubarwa gifise iteka ntangere
  37,108,Duca tumusigira kubaje munyuma yiwe
  37,109,Amahoro y’Imana abe kuntumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii)
  37,110,Uku niko duhemba abantu bagira ineza bose
  37,111,Ntankeka yari mubantu bacu bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  37,112,"Hanyuma\ttwamuciriye\tagace\tyuko\tazokwibaruka\tintumwa\ty’Imana Is’haqa (iii) n’intumwa muntumwa z’ abagira ineza"
  37,113,"Duca turamu hezagira hamwe n’intumwa y’Imana Is’haqa (iii) hamwe no muruvyaro rwabo, kuko aribo babaye mubagira ineza. hamwe n’abahemukiye imitima yabo bimwe bigaragara"
  37,114,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twarabagiriye impuhwe intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) hamwe n’intumwa y’Imana Haruna (iii)
  37,115,Duca turaba rokora hamwe n’abantu babo mugihe bari mungorane zidasanzwe
  37,116,Duca tubakingira nabo baca baba bene intsinzi nyakuri
  37,117,Bose uko ari babiri twabahaye igitabu gitanga umuco
  37,118,Duca turabarongora munzira igororotse
  37,119,Hanyuma duca tubasigira mubaje munyuma yabo
  37,120,Amahoro y’Imana abe kuntumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) hamwe na Haruna (iii)
  37,121,Ntankeka uku niko duhemba abagira ineza
  37,122,Ntankeka bari mubantu bacu bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  37,123,"Mu vy’ukuri, intumwa y’Imana Il’yaasiiyn (iii) yari muntumwa z’Imana"
  37,124,"Mugihe yabwira abantu biwe ati:- mbega mwebwe ntimutinya"
  37,125,"Mutabaza isanamu ryitwa Baa’la, mukareka gusaba umwiza wabaremyi"
  37,126,"Imana\tariyo\tmuremyi\twanyu\tn’Umuremyi\tw’abavyeyi\tbanyu\tbaho hambere"
  37,127,Baramu hakanye ntankeka rero bazo shengezwa mubihano
  37,128,Dukuyemwo abantu b’Imana basukuwe nayo nyene
  37,129,Twamusigiye kubaje munyuma yiwe
  37,130,Amahoro y’Imana abe kuntumwa y’Imana Il’yaasiiyn (iii)
  37,131,Ntankeka uku niko duhemba abagira ineza
  37,132,Mu vy’ukuri yari mubantu bacu bemera Imana yabo bimwe vy’ukuri
  37,133,Mu vy’ukuri intumwa y’Imana Lutwi (iii) yari muntumwa z’Imana
  37,134,Mugihe twamurokora hamwe n’abantu biwe bose
  37,135,Dukuye mwo umukenyezi ashaje mubasigaye inyuma
  37,136,Hanyuma niho twahonya abandi
  37,137,Mu vy’ukuri mwama mubacako mugitondo
  37,138,"No mw’ijoro nyene, mbega mwebwe ntimutegera"
  37,139,Mu vy’ukuri intumwa y’Imana Yunusu (iii) yari muntumwa z’Imana
  37,140,Mugihe yirukira mubwato bwikoreye ibintu vyinshi
  37,141,Baca bagira amatora aca aba mubatsinzwe nuguca atabwa mumazi
  37,142,Mukanya ifi ica iramumira mugihe yari muba taweko umwikomo
  37,143,Iyo ataba yari mubantu basenga Imana yiwe y’ukuri
  37,144,"Ntankeka\tyari\tkuguma\tmunda\ty’iyofi\tkugeza\tk’umusi\twizurwa ry’abantu bose"
  37,145,"Mugabo\ttwaciye\ttumujugunya\tkunkengera\tz’ikiyaga\tnawe\taremvye cane"
  37,146,Duca tumu nagishiriza uruyuzi rw’itango yaguma afungura
  37,147,Twaramutwaye ku bantu ibihumbi ijana n’abarenga
  37,148,"Baca baremera, nukuba nezereza kugeza kugihe caho basandabira"
  37,149,"Nimu\tbabaze\tmuti:-\tmbega\tUmuremyi\twawe\tniwe\tafise\tibibondo vy’abigeme nabo bakaba bafise ibibomdo vy’abahungu"
  37,150,"Mbega\ttwebwe\ttwaremye\tAbamarayika\tkuba\tyuko\taribo\tbakenyezi nabo bakaba ivyabona"
  37,151,Muragabe ku vyiyadukiza kuribo n’ivyo bavuga
  37,152,"Imana yaravyaye, mu vy’ukuri kuribo ntankeka n’ababeshi"
  37,153,Yoba yaratoye ibibondo vy’abigeme gusumba ibibondo vy’abahungu
  37,154,Mubayeho gute! Muca urubanza gute
  37,155,Yo! Mbega mwebwe aho muri ntimwibuka
  37,156,Canke mwebwe murafise ivyemezo biri k’umugaragaro
  37,157,Nimuzane igitabu canyu ni mwaba muvugisha ukuri
  37,158,"Nabo bashizeho imiryango hagati yabo n’ibisigo, n’ivyo bisigo vyari vyamaze kumenya yuko atankeka kuribo bazo shengezwa"
  37,159,Imana iri kure n’ingene bayihayagiza
  37,160,Dukuye mwo abantu beranda batowe n’Imana
  37,161,Rero ntankeka mwebwe hamwe nabo musenga
  37,162,Ntimushobora kuba zimiza
  37,163,Atari bamwe bazo kwinjira mu muriro udahera
  37,164,Ntan’umwe muri twebwe atari uko afise ubwicaro bwiwe buzwi
  37,165,Mu vy’ukuri muri twebwe harimwo abatonda ku mirongo
  37,166,Hariho n’abandi muri twebwe bahayagiza Imana y’ukuri
  37,167,Mu vy’ukuri bamye bavuga
  37,168,Iyo tuba dufise igitabu nkuko babifise ba bantu baho hambere
  37,169,Ntankeka twari kuba mu bantu beranda b’Imana bisukuye
  37,170,Ico gitabu baragi hakanye rero ubu vuba bazomenya
  37,171,Kandi ntankeka ijambo ryacu riramaze gushika ku bantu bacu bahawe ubutumwa
  37,172,Yuko aribo bazo rokorwa
  37,173,N’ingabo zacu nizo zizo tsinda
  37,174,Rero nimu bareke kure mu mwanya mutoyi gusa
  37,175,Kandi mu bitegereze gusa nabo ubu vuba bazobona
  37,176,Yoh! barahimiriza ibihano vyacu
  37,177,Rero mugihe bizo manuka kurubuga rwabo hazoba hari mugitondo kitari ciza ku bantu batujijwe
  37,178,Nimu bareke mumwanya mutoyi gusa
  37,179,"Nurabe gusa, nabone ubu vuba bazobona"
  37,180,"Umuremyi\twawe\tari\tkure\tnivyo,\tUmuremyi\tw’iteka\thamwe\tn’ivyo bayihayagiza ko"
  37,181,N’amahoro y’Imana asasagare kuntumwa z’Imana zose
  37,182,"Nihayagizwa ryose ryiza niry’Imana, Umuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose"
  38,1,"Swaad, (Insiguro y’iyi ndome hamwe n’uwufise ubumenyi bwayo bwose buzi Imana yonyene gusa). Ndarahiye kuri iyi Qur’aani ntagatifu ifise ubutumwa nyakuri"
  38,2,Mugabo abahakanye Umuremyi wabo bari mu bishima nugu higanwa
  38,3,"Twahoneje abantu bangahe imbere yabo, batako bakoma induru mugabo umwanya w’ukurokoka wamaze guhera"
  38,4,"Baratangaye mugihe bashikirwa n’uwutuza ava muribo hanyuma abatemera Imana yabo y’ukuri bavuze bati:- uyo muntu n’umurozi kandi n’umubeshi"
  38,5,"Yagize Imana zose kuba ari Imana imwe gusa, ntankeka iri n’ijambo ry’igitangaza"
  38,6,"Baciye bitahira bamwe mubakuru babo bavuga bati:- nimwigire kandi mwigumanire n’izo Mana zanyu, mu vy’ukuri iri n’ijambo rikenewe"
  38,7,"Twebwe ntitwigeze twumva ibi bintu yuko muri iyi migenzo yacu yanyuma, kandi ntivyamye ho ibi vyose atari uko ari ivyadutse gusa"
  38,8,"Niwe wenyene yamanuriwe ubu butumire gusa natwe ntitwabuhabwa, mugabo abo bantu bari bafise amakenga gusa kubera ubutumire bwanje, ahubwo ntibara honja ibihano vyanje"
  38,9,"Mbega barafise ububiko bw’imigisha y’Umuremyi wawe, nyene ubushobozi atanga vyose"
  38,10,"Canke barafise ubwami bw’Amajuru n’Isi hamwe n’ibiri hagati yavyo, rero nibafate inzira ibashikana yo"
  38,11,Izi n’ingabo zizo gendeshwa ningoga muvyondo vy’abahakanyi vyagendeshejwe ningoga aho hambere
  38,12,Abaho hambere barahakanye abantu bo kuntumwa y’Imana Nuhu (iii) nabo kuntumwa y’Imana Aadi (iii) na Fir’auni nyene amazu y’inkingi zikoma komeye
  38,13,Na Thamuda hamwe n’abantu bokwa Lutwi n’abantu bo mukibira c’ibiti vyinshi iyo niyo mirwi yabo
  38,14,"Abo bose bara hakanye intumwa z’Imana, rero ibihano vyanje vyaraba shikiye"
  38,15,N’aba ntibarindira atari akaruru kamwe gusa kukuzurwa kwabo kata rindiriza
  38,16,"Bama bavuga bati:- Muremyi wacu, nutuzanire bimwe mubihano vyacu imbere yuwo musi wugu harurwa"
  38,17,"Nutenyenye kuri ivyo bavuga, mugabo wibuke wa muntu wacu mweranda ariwe Daudi (iii) nyene inguvu, mu vy’ukuri yari umuntu agaruka ku Mana n’ubu gamburutsi"
  38,18,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twara gamburukiye imisozi hamwe nawe ininahaze kuva k’umugoroba no mugitondo
  38,19,Hamwe n’inyoni zegereranijwe hamwe n’izindi zose zara mugamburukira
  38,20,Duca dushira mubwami bwiwe ubushobozi nukumuha ubumenyi bw’ugucira imanza abantu
  38,21,Mbega warashikiwe n’inkuru z’abari mumatati baca basimbira mucumba c’intumwa y’Imana Daudi (iii)
  38,22,"Mugihe binjira kwa Daudi (iii) yarabatinye nabo baca bavuga bati:- ntutinye kuri twebwe turi mumatati, umwe muri twebwe yarahemukiye mugenzi wiwe, none nuducire urubanza rw’ukuri, kandi ntuhengame ahanaka kandi uturongore munzira igororotse"
  38,23,"Mu vy’ukuri uyu ni mwene wanje, afise intama z’inyana mirongo icenda n’icenda, nanje nkaba mfise inyana imwe gusa mugabo yavuze ati ndamuhe iyi rwanje ayitungire, none yananiye mu majambo"
  38,24,"Avuga ati:- ni vy’ukuri yaguhemukiye mukugusaba iyo ntungwa yawe mukwongereza kuntungwa ziwe, ntankeka abari mw’ishirahamwe benshi bama bahemukirana bamwe kubandi dukuyemwo abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri nukugira ibikorwa vyiza, nabo bantu bari kurushi, mu mwanya intumwa y’Imana Daudi (iii) yabona yuko twamuhaye ikibazo, aca asaba ikigongwe ku Muremyi wiwe n’ugupfukama n’ubwitonzi ntangere nugu tumbera ku Muremyi wiwe"
  38,25,"Duca tumugirira ikigongwe kuri ivyo vyose, mu vy’ukuri arafise kuri twebwe icubahiro kininiya n’ahantu heza"
  38,26,"Ewe Daudi (iii) mu vy’ukuri twebwe twaguhaye ubutegetsi ng’aha kw’Isi, rero nubacire abo bantu urubanza rw’ukuri kandi ntukurikire ivyo umutima wawe ushatse ntuze ukuzimize munzira nziza y’Imana, mu vy’ukuri bamwe bazimira nuguta inzira y’Imana abo bantu bazoronka ibihano bikaze cane kubera ukwibagira kwabo wa musi wuguharurwa"
  38,27,"Kandi twebwe ntitwaremye Amajuru n’Isi hamwe n’ibirimwo vyose kubusa gusa, ibi vyose nivyo bikeka bamwe batemera Imana yabo y’ukuri, rero ibihano bikaze cane vy’umuriro udahera bizoba shikira bamwe bahakana Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  38,28,"Mbega tubagire bamwe bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri nukugira ibikorwa vyiza yuko boba bangana n’abononyi bagira ubwo bwononyi ng’aha kw’Isi, canke tubagire aba gamburukira Imana ko bangana n’abononyi"
  38,29,"Iki gitabu twakimanuye kuri wewe, kikaba gifise imihezagiro myinshi cane kugira ngo abantu bategere neza, iyumvire amajambo yaco hamwe n’abafise ubwenge nabo bategere neza"
  38,30,"Twarahaye intumwa y’Imana Daudi (iii) ikibondo citwa Suleymanu (iii) akaba yari mu bantu beza, kandi akaba yari afise n’ubwitonzi ntangere"
  38,31,Mugihe bwagoroba yashikirijwe Ifarasi zihumuye zihagaze nazo zikaba zari zihwahutse mugihe zitegetswe kwiruka
  38,32,"Yaciye avuga ati:- jewe nkunda ibintu vyiza mukwibuka Umuremyi wanje, mu nyuma zafarasi zinyegeza inyuma y’uruzitiro"
  38,33,"Nimu bagarure iwanje, hanyuma aca atangura kuzi hanagura kumaguru yazo no kumazosi yazo"
  38,34,Twaramuhaye intumwa y’Imana Suleymanu (iii) duca dushiraho uwundi mubiri hejuru y’inyegamo yiwe hanyuma aragaruka wenyene
  38,35,"Aca avuga ati:- Muremyi wanje, nungirire ikigongwe kandi umpe n’ubwami, kandi ntuze ubuhe uwariwe wese munyuma zanje, ntankeka ni wewe mutanzi wa vyose"
  38,36,"Duca tumu gamburukiza umuyaga ugenda buhoro buhoro kw’itegeko ryiwe, naho ushaka gushika hose"
  38,37,Hamwe n’ibisigo n’abubatsi n’abibira mumazi
  38,38,N’ibindi bisigo biboshwe n’iminyororo
  38,39,"Iyi n’ingabirano yacu twaguhaye tutarinze guharurirana, rero nuyitange canke uyigumye utarinze kugiriranira ibiharuro"
  38,40,Mu vy’ukuri arafise kuri twebwe icubahiro n’ahantu heza
  38,41,"Kandi mwibuke intumwa yacu y’Imana Ayyubu (iii) mugihe Umuremyi wiwe yamuhamagara avuga ati:- mu vy’ukuri Shetani yanshikirije ibishoboka hamwe n’ingorane"
  38,42,"Ihute nuku kuguru kwawe, naya niyo mazi apfuse yukwisukira hamwe n’ayandi yukunywa"
  38,43,Duca tumuha abantu biwe hamwe n’abandi nkabo hamwe nabo kumigisha ivuye iwacu hamwe n’ubutumwa ku bantu bafise ubwenge
  38,44,"Nufate amasonga y’uduti mukuboko kwawe, hunyuma uce umukubitisha umucance wawe, kandi ntute indahiro yawe, ntankeka twebwe twamusanze ari mu bantu batekereje kandi n’intore, mu vy’ukuri yari muba gamburutsi bacane"
  38,45,Bibuke abantu bacu ariyo ntumwa yacu y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii) na Is’haqa n’intumwa y’Imana na Yaaqubu bari bafise ubushobozi n’ubwenge buhagije
  38,46,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twagutoye kuri ryajambo ryiza cane ryukwibuka umusi w’imperuka
  38,47,"Kandi ntankeka abamyeho imbere yacu, nabo nimu bantu beza batowe"
  38,48,Kandi mwibuke intumwa y’Imana Ismaaili (iii) hamwe n’intumwa y’Imana Al’yasaa (iii) n’intumwa y’Imana Dhul’qiflu (iii) n’abo bose bari mu bantu b’intungane
  38,49,Ubu n’ubwibutso mu vy’ukuri abatinya Imana yabo y’ukuri igituro cabo caho bazo garukira hazoba heza cane
  38,50,Imirima yukwicara mwo mubuzima bwabo bwose izoba yuguruye imiryango yayo kubera bo gusa
  38,51,Bazo kwegamira kunyegamo basaba ivyamwa vyinshi hamwe n’ibinyobwa
  38,52,Hamwe nabo bazoba ho n’abanega babo bahumurije amaso yabo kubatambukanyi babo
  38,53,Ibi nivyo mwaraganiwe k’umusi w’imperuka
  38,54,Mu vy’ukuri iyi niyo migisha yacu idahera
  38,55,Nuko rero mu vy’ukuri bamwe barenga imbibe ingaruka zabo zizoba ziri ahantu habi cane
  38,56,Wamuriro witiriwe Jahannamu niwo bazokwinjiramwo naho nahateguwe nabi cane
  38,57,N’uku bizoba rero nibahonje amazi y’amarike n’amashira
  38,58,N’ibindi bihano nk’ibi ni vyinshi
  38,59,"Izi nizo ngabo zizo kwinjira hamwe namwe, mugabo ntizaronse ahantu heza zishikira mugabo zizo kwinjira mu muriro udahera"
  38,60,"Bavuze bati:- mwebwe ntakaze ryiza mufise mwebwe nimwe mwatumye turonka ibihano aho naho n’ahantu h’ubwicaro bubi cane"
  38,61,"Bavuze bati:- Muremyi wacu, abatumye tugira ibi vyose, n’ubongereze ibihano vy’incuro zibiri iyo mu muriro udahera"
  38,62,"Bazovuga\tbati:-\tvyabaye\tgute\tko\ttutababona\tbabantu\ttwahora tubaharura ko bari mu bantu babi"
  38,63,Erega twaraba kengereye mugabo amaso yacu ntiyababona gusa
  38,64,Ntankeka ibi bintu vy’amatati y’abantu bo mumuriro udahera nay’ukuri
  38,65,"Vuga\tuti:-\tmu\tvy’ukuri\tjewe\tnd’uwutuza\tgusa,\tkandi\tntayindi\tMana itegerezwa gusengwa atariyo yonyene rudende nyene ubushobozi"
  38,66,Umumenyi w’Amajuru n’Isi hamwe nibirimwo vyose nyene ubushobozi hamwe n’ikigongwe cinshi
  38,67,"Vuga uti:- izi n’inkuru zihambaye cane"
  38,68,Mutitayeho namba
  38,69,Ntabumenyi nari mfise bw’ibiremwa bitagatifu mugihe batumvikana
  38,70,Simbwirwa ikintu na kimwe kuri jewe atari uko nd’umuntu atuza abantu kandi mboneka
  38,71,"Umuremyi wawe mugihe yababwira Abamarayika ati:- mu vy’ukuri jewe nzorema umuntu ndamukuye mw’ivu"
  38,72,"Ninarangiza kurema uyo muntu nukumu huhera umutima uvuye\tkuri jewe, rero nimuce mumupfukamira nukumu gamburukira"
  38,73,Bara gamburutse Abamarayika bose uko bangana bose
  38,74,Dukuyemwo uwitwa Ibilisi yishimye nukuba muba hakanyi b’Imana
  38,75,"Imana yamubwiye iti:- ewe Ibilisi, n’igiki cakubujje ku gamburukira uwo naremye ku maboko yanje, mbega winamuye canke wabaye mubantu bakuru"
  38,76,"Nawe yishura ati:- jewe ndimwiza gusumba uyo waremye, kuko jewe wandemye unkuye mu muriro udahera, nawe umurema umukuye mw’ivu"
  38,77,"Imana\tica\tivuga\titi:-\tnuve\tmuri\tuwo\tmuriro\tudahera\tkuko\turamaze gutabwa kure n’imigisha yanje"
  38,78,Mu vy’ukuri umuvumo wanje uzoba hejuru yawe kuri kugeza k’umusi w’imperuka
  38,79,"Nawe yishura ati:- Muremyi wanje, numpe umwanya na mutoyi gusa kugeza k’umusi bazozurwa ibiremwa vyose"
  38,80,"Imana imubwira iti:- nivyo wewe uri mubaronse ikibanza c’ukubaho"
  38,81,Kugeza kumwanya w’umusi wategekanijwe
  38,82,"Nawe yishura ati:- ndarahiye k’ukuri kw’iteka ryawe ntankeka jewe abo bantu bawe nzobazimiza uko bangana bose"
  38,83,Dukuye mwo ba bantu bawe muribo ar’intore
  38,84,"Imana ivuga iti:- ndarahiye mvugishije ukuri"
  38,85,Mu vy’ukuri jewe nzokwuzuza mu muriro udahera kuri wewe Shetani hamwe n’abagu kurikira muribo
  38,86,"Vuga uti:- jewe sindaba saba impembo kuri ibi, kandi jewe sindi mu bantu bitegeka"
  38,87,Ntivyari kuba ibi vyose atari uko ari ubutumwa ku bantu bose
  38,88,Kandi ntankeka mwebwe muzomenya inkuru ziwe mumwanya
  39,1,Imanuka ry’iki gitabu gitagatifu nikivuye ku Mana nyene ubushobozi hamwe n’ubuhizi buhagije
  39,2,"Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twaku manuriye iki gitabu bimwe vy’ukuri, rero n’usenge Imana yawe nukuyigira yuko ariyo Muremyi wenyene gusa"
  39,3,"Uwizerwa w’Umuremyi n’Imana yonyene gusa, mugabo bamwe bagira abandi kuba arizo Mana aho kuba ariyo yonyene rudende bavuga bati:- twebwe abo ntituba senga mugabo niba dushikane hafi cane y’Imana, mu vy’ukuri Imana izocira urubanza ruri hagati yabo kuvyo batumvikanye ko, ntankeka Imana ntirongora umubeshi w’umuhakanyi w’Imana"
  39,4,"Iyo Imana ibishaka ngo ironke ikibondo ntankeka yari gutora uwo yishakiye mubo yiremeye, mugabo iri kure yivyo vyose kuko n’Imana imwe yonyene rudende igira ivyo yishakiye"
  39,5,"Niyo yaremye Amajuru n’Isi bimwe vy’ukuri, ikaba ariyo yapfuse Ijoro hejuru y’Umutaga kandi ikaba ariyo yapfuse Umutaga hejuru y’Ijoro kandi ikaba ariyo yagamburukije Izuba n’Ukwezi vyose bikagira gusa kugihe categekanijwe, mumenye yuko ariyo nyene ubushobozi kandi ariyo nyene ikigongwe cinshi"
  39,6,"Niyo yabaremye mu mutima umwe, hanyuma igira mugenziwe kuba nkawe nukuba manurira ibikoko umunani harimwo impfizi n’inyana, rero ibarema munda z’abavyeyi banyu mufise iremwa ritandukanye n’irindi, riri mumyijima itatu, iyo rero niyo Mana ariyo Muremyi wanyu, ubwami bwose ni rwiwe kandi ntawundi asengwa bimwe vy’ukuri atariyo yonyene gusa, none mwebwe muhindukizwa hehe"
  39,7,"Ni mwaba muri ahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri, Imana ntibakeneye mwebwe mugabo ntiyemera ubuhakanyi bw’abantu bayo beranda, rero nimwa shima ivyo nivyo biyinezereza kuko biba bivuye kuri mwebwe, n’uwikorera ntazo kwikorera itu ry’uwundi, hanyuma ingaruka yanyu niku Muremyi wanyu, niyo izoba bwira ivyo mwahora mugira, ntankeka niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ibiri mubikiriza vyanyu"
  39,8,"Mugihe umuntu ashikiwe n’ingorane yama atakambira Umuremyi wiwe nugu tumbera iwe, hanyuma imuhaye imigisha ivuye kuriyo, wa muntu aca yibagira kuvyo yahora imu hamagarira aho hambere hahise nukuyi gereranya n’ibindi bintu kugira ngo ibatakaze munzira yayo, wewe rero nuvuge uti:- nunezerwe kubera ubuhakanyi bwawe mukiringo gitoyi gusa kuko wewe uzoba uri mu bantu bo mumuriro udahera"
  39,9,"Mbega agire amasengesho mumyanya y’ijoro nugupfukama hamwe nuguhagarara nugutinya uwo musi w’imperuka hamwe nukwizera imigisha y’Umuremyi wiwe, wewe vuga uti:- mbega boshobora kungana bamwe bafise ubumenyi nabamwe badafise ubumenyi, rero abikebura nibarya bafise ubwenge gusa"
  39,10,"Vuga uti:- mwebwe bantu banje bemeye Imana y’ukuri, ni mutinye Umuremyi wanyu, bamwe bagira ineza iyariyo yose ng’aha kw’isi bazoronswa ivyiza\tvyabo,\tn’Isi\ty’Imana\tiragutse\tcane,\tkandi\tntankeka\tabatenyenya bazoronswa impembo yabo batarinze kurimburirana n’Imana"
  39,11,"Vuga uti:- mu vy’ukuri jewe nategetswe yuko nsenga Imana nukwizera yuko Umuremyi ariwe wenyene gusa"
  39,12,Kandi nategetswe ngombe ndimu bantu bambere biyemeje kuba ndi umu Isilamu
  39,13,"Vuga uti:- jewe ntinya ibihano vy’umusi mukuru mugihe no cumurira Umuremyi wanje"
  39,14,"Vuga uti:- jewe nsenga Imana yanje nemeza yuko ariyo yonyene gusa kandi ariyo Mana"
  39,15,"Rero mwebwe nimusenge muvyo mukunda bitari Imana, nawe nuvuge iti:- mu vy’ukuri abazo ronka uruhombo nibarya bataye imitima yabo muruhombo hamwe n’abantu babo k’umusi w’imperuka, ni murabe urwo nirwo ruhombo ruri k’umugaragaro"
  39,16,"Hazoshirwa hejuru yabo ibicu vy’umuriro no munsi yabo hazobayo ibindi bicu, kuri ivyo rero Imana irabagabisha abantu bayo, namwe bantu banje nimutinye"
  39,17,"Na bamwe batitaho mukugira amasengesho y’amasanamu nuku gamburukira Imana, inkuru nziza nirwabo rero nubahe inkuru nziza aba bantu banje"
  39,18,"Nabumviriza amajambo bagakurikira ayafise akamaro kuribo abo bantu nibo Imana yarongoye, kandi nibo bafise ubwenge"
  39,19,"Mbega uwategerejwe gucirirwa urubanza rw’ibihano, mbega woshobora kurokora uwuri mumuriro udahera"
  39,20,"Mugabo aba gamburukiye Umuremyi wabo bazoronka amazu maremare agerekeranye kuyandi mazu maremare, munsi yayo mazu hazocamwo inzuzi, iyo niyo ndagano y’Imana, kuko Imana ntirenga kundagano yayo"
  39,21,"Mbega ntubona yuko Imana yamanuye amazi iyakuye mubicu hanyuma iyacisha hasi, nukuba amasoko y’amazi ari mukuzimu, hanyuma inagisha ivyamwa vy’ubwoko butandukanye, rero uca ubona ivyo vyamwa vyumutse nuguhindura amabara y’umuhondo, hanyuma bigaca bitangura gucika gurika, ntankeka muri ibi vyose harimwo ivyibutso ku bantu bafise ubwenge"
  39,22,"Mbega umuntu Imana yugururiye igikiriza ciwe nukwemera ubu Isilamu kandi akaba ari mumuco uvuye ku Muremyi wiwe, rero ibihano bikaze cane bizoshikira bamwe bafise imitima y’agatimatare batibuka Imana namba, aba kandi nibo bari mubuzimire buri k’umugaragaro"
  39,23,"Imana yamanuye amajambo meza cane arico gitabu kirimwo amajambo ahuje n’ayandi kandi aguma asubirwamwo, urukoba rw’umubiri narwo rwama ruhinda agashitsi kuri barya batinya Umuremyi wabo, hanyuma urukoba rwabo narwo hamwe n’imitima yabo iguma ihwahutse mukwibuka Umuremyi wabo, ubwo nibwo burokoke bw’Imana, kuri ubwo burokoke irongora uwo yishakiye, kandi uwurekuriwe n’Imana yuko yazimiye, ntankundi rero uwo muntu ntawuzo murongora"
  39,24,"Mbega uwuzoba akingiye amaso yiwe n’ibihano bibi vyo k’umusi w’imperuka nayo abahemukiye imitima yabo bazobwirwa bati:- nimuhonje kuvyo mwamuye"
  39,25,"Abamyeho imbere yabo barahakanye, n’ibihano vyaraba shikiye bivuye ahantu batazi"
  39,26,Imana yaciye ibahonjesha ibimaramare mubuzima bwo ng’aha kw’Isi n’ibihano vyo k’umusi w’imperuka nivyo bininiya iyo bobimenya
  39,27,Ntankeka abantu twaraberetse uburorero butagira uko bungana buri muri iki gitabu gitagatifu ca Qur’aani kugira ngo abantu bagume bibuka
  39,28,Iyi Qur’aani ntagatifu yamanutse mururimi rw’icarabu itarimwo ibintu bihuvya kugira ngo bikingire
  39,29,"Imana ibatangirako uburorero bw’umuntu afise basebuja bari mumatati, n’uwundi muntu afise Sebuja wiwe umwe wenyene gusa, mbega ubona yuko bongana mubuzima bwabo n’ugushimira Imana, mugabo benshi muribo ntavyo bazi"
  39,30,"Mu vy’ukuri wewe uzosandaba, nabo nyene bazosandaba"
  39,31,Hanyuma ntankeka muzo kwitwara k’umusi w’imperuka imbere y’Umuremyi wanyu
  39,32,"Ni nde yoba ari umuhemu yahemukiye umutima wiwe gusumba uwubeshera Imana nuguhakana ukuri kwama mugihe kwamushikiye, none simuri wa muriro udahera aribwo bwicaro bwabo bahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri"
  39,33,"Nuwazanye ukuri nuku kwemeza, abo bantu nibo bagamburukira Imana yabo"
  39,34,"Bazoronka ivyo bipfuza vyose ku Muremyi wabo, iyo niyo mpembo yabakora ibikorwa vyiza"
  39,35,Kugira ngo Imana ibahana gurire amabi yabo yose bagize nukubariha impembo yabo kuvyiza bahora bagira
  39,36,"Mbega Imana ntihagiza umuntu wayo, kandi baragutera ubwoba kuri barya mutari kumwe nabo rero uwaciriwe urubanza n’Imana yuko atakara ntawundi muntu yomu rongora"
  39,37,"Nuwo Imana yarongoye ntawu shobora kumutakaza, mbega Imana siyo nyene ubushobozi ishobora kwihorera"
  39,38,"Ubajije uti :- mbega ni nde yaremye Amajuru n’Isi, ntankeka bazokwishura bavuga bati :- n’Imana, nawe nubishure uti :- mbega mwebwe mubona gute muri bamwe musaba atari Imana y’ukuri, yuko Imana ishatse kungirira inabi, mbega barashobora kunkurira izo ngorane ziwe, canke ishatse kumpezagira mbega nibo bashobora gukingira imigisha yayo ? wewe nuvuge uti :- jewe Imana irampagije ni kuriyo bizera abayizera"
  39,39,"Vuga uti :- mwebwe bantu banje, ni mugire ibikorwa vyanyu mutekereje nanje nuko nyene ndiko ndakora, rero ubu vuba muzobimenya"
  39,40,Ninde azo shikirwa n’ibihano bizomu tetereza hamwe nibizo manukira kuriwe kandi bibandanya
  39,41,"Twebwe twakumanuriye iki gitabu gitagatifu ca Qur’aani kubera abantu bose, kandi kugira ngo uba sobanurire ukuri, rero uwuzo rongoka ni kukamaro k’umutima wiwe, nayo uwuzo takara azo takara ntankeka azoba atakaye k’uruhombo rw’umutima wiwe, na wewe nturi mu bantu baba cungera"
  39,42,"Imana niyo yica imitima y’abantu kumwanya w’urupfu rwayo, n’iyindi mitima itarapfa iri mw’itiro ryayo, rero ica igumya ya mitima yandikiwe urupfu hanyuma igaca isubiriza yayindi kugeza kumwanya wagenewe, ntankeka muri ibi vyose hariho icirwa ku bantu biyumvira"
  39,43,"Canke nibo bigiriye ababa sabira imbere y’Imana? Wewe nuvuge uti:- naho ata butegetsi bafise bw’ikintu na kimwe kandi ntabumenyi bafise"
  39,44,"Vuge uti :- isabirwa ryose riri kw’itegeko ry’Imana kuko ariyo nyene ubwami bw’Amajuru n’Isi, hanyuma mwese muzo subizwa iwe"
  39,45,"Mugihe havuzwe Imana yonyene rudende, imitima yabamwe batemera umusi w’imperuka ica ishavura, no mugihe havuzwe abatavuga rumwe nabo mumwanya uca ubona banezerewe"
  39,46,"Vuga uti:- ewe Muremyi waremye Amajuru n’Isi, ufise ubumenyi bw’ibintu bitaboneka n’ibiboneka, ni wewe uzocira urubanza ruzoba ruri hagati y’abantu bawe kuvyo bahora batumvikana ko"
  39,47,"Niba abahemukiye imitima yabo iyo boba bafise ibiri ng’aha kw’Isi n’ibindi nk’ivyo, ntankeka bari gutanga kugira ngo bikombore kubijanye n’ibihano bibi vy’umusi w’imperuka, kandi bizo garagazwa ku Mana kuvyo batari bizeye"
  39,48,"Hazo bonekana amabi yabimwe bahora bagira, kandi bazo kikuzwa nivyo bahora bafata minenerwe"
  39,49,"Ingorane ishikiye umuntu aca adusaba twebwe, hanyuma tumuhaye imigisha ivuye iwacu aca avuga ati:- ibi ndabihawe kubera ubumenyi bwanje none sivyo, ico n’ikibazo mugabo benshi muribo ntakintu na kimwe bazi"
  39,50,Barayavuze aya majambo abamyeho imbere yabo mugabo ntaco vyabamariye muvyo bahora bagira
  39,51,"Rero barahuye n’amabi yivyo bakoze, n’abahemukiye imitima yabo muri aba, ubu vuba nabone bazohura n’amabi bahora bagira, nabo s’abazo nanirana"
  39,52,"Mbega ntibazi yuko Imana itanga imigisha yayo kuwo yishakiye nukwima uwo yishakiye, mu vy’ukuri muri ibi vyose harimwo ibintu vy’ugutegera ku bantu bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  39,53,"Vuga uti :- mwebwe bantu banje mwahemukiye imitima yanyu, ntimu debukirwe kumigisha y’Imana, ntankeka Imana yama igira ikigongwe kubicumuro vyose, mu vy’ukuri niyo ifise ikigongwe cinshi kandi niyo nyene impuhwe zihagije"
  39,54,Nimu garuke ku Muremyi wanyu kandi muyi gamburukire imbere yuko mushikirwa n’ibihano vy’Imana hanyuma ntimuzo ronka umufasha
  39,55,Nimu kurikire ibintu vyiza muvya manuwe kuri mwebwe bivuye ku muremyi wanyu imbere yugu shikirwa n’ibihano bije giturumbuka namwe mutabizi
  39,56,"Ntuze uvuge umutima w’umuntu uti:- ewe maganya yanje kuvyo nagabanije kuruhande rw’Imana, mu vy’ukuri jewe nari mubantu bafata ibintu minenerwe"
  39,57,"Canke niyavuga iti:- iyo Imana indongora, ntankeka nari kuba mu bantu batakambira Imana"
  39,58,"Canke ikavuga mugihe ibonye ibihano:- iyo ndonka ingaruka nari kuba mubagira ineza"
  39,59,Ni vy’ukuri kandi ntankeka warashikiwe n’amajambo yanje uraya hakana k’umugaragaro nu kwishima hanyuma uca uba muba hakanyi b’Imana
  39,60,"No k’umusi w’imperuka uzoba bona bamwe babesheye Imana mumaso yabo hamaze kwirabura, mbega simu muriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu ariho hazoba ubwicaro bwabamye bishima"
  39,61,"N’Imana izoba rokora bamwe bayitinya kubera intsinzi yabo, kandi ntibazo korwako n’amabi canke ntibazo teterezwa"
  39,62,Imana niyo rurema rw’ibintu vyose kandi niyo mureretsi w’ibiri hejuru y’ibintu vyose
  39,63,Impfunguruzo z’Amajuru n’Isi zose ziri ku Mana nabamwe bahakanye amajambo y’Imana abo nibo bari muruhombo runiniya
  39,64,"Vuga uti:- mbega muntegetse gusenga uwutari Imana mwabijuju mwe"
  39,65,"Mu vy’ukuri wewe warugururiwe hamwe n’abari imbere yawe yuko niwa gereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu ntankeka ibikorwa vyawe bizoba bibaye ivy’impfagusa, kandi ningombwa uzoba uri mu bantu bari muruhombo"
  39,66,Ahubwo wewe n’usenge Imana yawe gusa kandi ube mu bantu bashima
  39,67,"Ntibasoneye Imana yabo bimwe bikwiye, no k’umusi w’imperuka Isi yose izoba iri muminwe yayo, n’Amajuru yose azo zingirwa mukuboko kwayo kw’iburyo, nayo ikaba itandukanye nuku gabanukirwa n’ikintu icarico cose, kandi niyo iri hejuru gusumba kuvyo bayi gereraniriza ko"
  39,68,"Hazovuzwa inzamba hace havamwo imitima y’abantu bari mumajuru hamwe nabari kw’Isi dukuyemwo uwo Imana yikundiye, hanyuma hazovuzwa iyindi nzamba igira kabiri aho rero niho hazozuka ibiremwa vyose bagume barabana gusa"
  39,69,"N’Isi izosa yangana k’umuco w’Umuremyi wayo, n’ibitabu vyose bizobikwa hanyuma hace hazanwa intumwa z’Imana n’ivyabona vyazo, hanyuma hazocibwa urubanza ruzoba ruri hagati yabo bimwe vy’ukuri, kandi ntibazo hemukirwa"
  39,70,N’umutima wu mw’umwe wese uzorihwa kuvyo wakoze nayo niyo ifise ubumenyi buhanitse bw’ivyo bagira vyose
  39,71,"N’abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri bazojanwa mumuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu bari imirwi n’iyindi kugeza naho bazoyishikira yugururwe imiryango yayo n’abacungereye uwo muriro bazobwirwa bati:- mbega ntimwashikiwe n’intumwa z’Imana ziri muri mwebwe ziba somera amajambo y’Umuremyi wanyu nukuba tuza kw’ihuriro ry’uwo musi wanyu, nabone bazovuga bati:- nukubera iki? mugabo ryaremejwe ijambo ry’ibihano rizoba kuri bamwe bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  39,72,"Hazovugwa hati:- ni mwinjire muri iyo myugariro y’uwo muriro udahera hanyuma muce mwicarayo, mugabo ubwo bwicaro bumeze gute, bwabo bantu bishima"
  39,73,"N’abemeye Umuremyi wabo bimwe biboneka bazojanwa mw’ijuru bari imirwi n’iyindi kugeza naho bazoshikira imyugariro yaho yamaze kwugururwa naba cungereye bazoba bwira bati:- amahoro y’Imana abe kuri mwebwe, kandi ni munezerwe, kandi mwinjire ng’aha mw’ijuru mubeho muzima bwanyu bwose"
  39,74,"Nabo bazovuga bati:- ihayagizwa ryose ni ry’Imana kuko ariyo iri mw’ijuru kandi ikaba ariyo yatwemereye indagano yayo hamwe nukudusigira ibisigi vy’Isi tuzokwicara muri iyo mirima aho dushaka hose, rero n’impembo nziza zimeze gute z’abagize ibikorwa vyiza"
  39,75,"Uzobona Abamarayika bakikuza hambavu y’inyegamo y’Imana bahayagiza nugu himbaza Umuremyi wabo, hakazo cibwaho n’urubanza ruzoba hagati yabo rw’ukuri kandi hazovurwa hati:- amahayagizwa yose meza nay’Imana Umuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose"
  40,1,"Ha, Miiym. (Insiguro yizi ndome hamwe nuwufise ubumenyi bwazo zose n’Imana yonyene gusa)"
  40,2,Ukumanurwa kw’iki gitabu gitagatifu c’Imana bivana n’Imana nyene ubushobozi n’ubumenyi buhagije
  40,3,"Niyo ihanagura ibicumuro nukwakira imbabazi z’abantu kandi irakaze cane muguhana kwayo, kandi niyo nyene ubutore, kandi ntayindi Mana isengwa bimwe vy’ukuri atariyo yonyene gusa, n’ingaruka yavyose iri kuriwe"
  40,4,Ntibaharira kumajambo y’Imana matagatifu atari abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri rero ntuhendwe nukugenda genda kwabo mubisagara
  40,5,"Abantu bo kuntumwa y’Imana Nuhu (iii) imbere yabo hamwe n’imirwi yabo munyuma yabo hamwe n’ayandi makungu barateguye umugambi w’amabi kuntumwa yabo y’Imana kugira ngo bayifate, hanyuma bayi gandagure, rero baraharira kubitajanye n’ukuri kugira ngo bahindure ukuri, kuri ivyo naciye ndabafata n’amaboko yanje, mbega ibihano vyanje vyari bimeze gute"
  40,6,Uku rero niko bashikiwe abo batemera Imana yabo y’ukuri kw’ijambo ry’Umuremyi wawe yuko ari abantu bo mumuriro udahera
  40,7,"Bamwe barerura inyegamo y’Imana y’iteka hamwe n’abayikikuje bose baninahaza Umuremyi wabo nukuyi takambira kandi barayemera bimwe vy’ukuri nababa sabira ikigongwe bemeye bimwe vy’ukuri bavuga bati:- Murenyi wacu ukwiye kubintu vyose no kumigisha yawe hamwe n’ubumenyi buhagije, nubagirire ikigongwe abo bantu bakigusavye ico kigongwe nugu kurikira inzira yawe kandi nuba kingire n’ibihano vyo mumuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu"
  40,8,"Muremyi wacu, nubinjize mumirima yubudahera wabemereye, kandi ubahe n’ibi mubagize ivyiza mu bavyeyi babo hamwe n’abatambukanyi babo n’ibondo vyabo, ntankeka ni wewe nyene ubushobozi n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  40,9,Kandi ubakingire n’ivyago kuko uwo ukingiye n’ivyo vyago kuri uwo musi mu vy’ukuri wewe uzoba wamuhezagiye nuko rero iyo niyo ntsinzi niniya
  40,10,"Mu vy’ukuri bamwe bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri bazobwirwa bati:- ntankeka ukubanka kw’Imana ni kunini cane gusumba ukwiyanka kw’imitima yanyu mugihe mwahamagarwa ngo mube aba Isilamu b’ukuri namwe murahakana"
  40,11,"Bazovuga bati:- Muremyi wacu, utwishe incuro zibiri usubira kutuzura izindi ncuro zibiri, rero natwe turemeye ibihano vyacu, mbega hari iyindi nzira yuguca mwo"
  40,12,"Kubera yuko mugihe bahora bayivuga Imana yonyene gusa mwaca mwanka, mugabo igereranijwe n’ibindi bintu mwaca muvyemera, rero umucamanza wuno musi n’Imana iri hejuru yavyose kandi ariyo nkuru"
  40,13,"Imana niyo izo bereka ibimenyetso vyayo hamwe nukuba manurira imigisha ivuye mw’ijuru, rero ntawibuka atari uwugarutse ku Mana yiwe"
  40,14,"Rero ni muyisabe Imana, kandi muyigirire yo nyene ibisabisho vyanyu naho abo bahakanyi b’Imana yabo y’ukuri bazoshavura"
  40,15,"Niyo nyene ubutegetsi buri hejuru cane, ikaba ishikiriza ubutumwa bw’amategeko kuwo yishakiye kubantu bayo beranda kugira ngo ubatuze k’umusi w’ihuriro ry’abantu bose"
  40,16,"Umusi bazo bonekana imbere y’Imana, kandi ntankuru iyariyo yose izo kwinyegeza imbere y’Imana, no kuri uno musi ubwami bw’Imana buzoba ari ubwande? Nu bw’Imana wenyene rudende ariwe nyene ubushobozi buhagije"
  40,17,"Uno musi umuntu wese azoronswa impembo yiwe kuvyo yakoreye ntawuzo hemukirwa uno musi, ntankeka Imana irafise umwete wuguharura"
  40,18,"Nubatuze k’umusi uri hafi cane wugushika, mugihe imitima yabo izoba yamaze gushika kunkoratima nayo yuzuyemwo ibimaramare, rero abahemukiye imitima yabo ntabagenzi bazoba bafise canke uwuzoba sabira canke uwuzo gamburukirwa"
  40,19,Niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ubuhemu bw’amaso yabo hamwe nivyo ibikiriza vyabo binyegeje
  40,20,N’Imana yama ica urubanza rw’ukuri mugabo bamwe basenga ibitari Imana y’ukuri ntabuca manza bazoba bafise mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo yumva nuku bona
  40,21,"Mbega ntibagize ingendo zo ng’aha kw’Isi ngo bitegereze ingene yabaye impera n’imperuka y’ababaye ho imbere yabo? Bari bafise ubushobozi buhagije n’ububasha bukwiye ng’aha kw’Isi kubasumba n’Imana niyo yabashize mubiganza vyayo kubera ibicumuro vyabo, kandi ntibari bafise uwubakingira n’Imana"
  40,22,"Ivyo nuko bahora bashikirwa n’intumwa z’Imana zifise n’ivyemezo biri k’umugaragaro mugabo barabahakanye ari naho Imana yabahanye, ntankeka niyo nyene ububasha, kandi niyo ikaze cane muguhana"
  40,23,Mu vy’ukuri twararungitse intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) hamwe n’ibitangaro vyacu hamwe n’ivyemezo biri k’umugaragaro
  40,24,"Nokwa Fir’auni hamwe no kwa Hamana na Qaaruni nibo baciye bavuga bati:- uwo muntu n’umurozi kandi n’umubeshi karuhariwe"
  40,25,"Mugihe yabashikiriza ukuri kwama kuje kuva iwacu baciye bavuga bati:- nimugandagure ibibondo vy’abahungu vyose hamwe nabamwemeye bose hanyuma muze musigaze abakanyezi babo gusa nayo ingeso z’abatemera Imana yabo y’ukuri ntiziba atari uko vyama ari ivyimpfagusa"
  40,26,"Fir’auni yavuze ati:- ni mundeke ndamu gandagure uyo Mussa (iii) hanyuma ace ahamagara Umuremyi wiwe amukingire, jewe Fir’auni ndafise amakenga yuko atazo kwonona idini ryanyu, canke ntaze kuzana umudugararo ngaha kw’Isi"
  40,27,"Intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) imwishura iti:- jewe ndikinze ku Muremyi wanje hamwe n’Umuremyi wanyu aze ankingire n’umuntu uwariwe wese yishima kandi atemera umusi uhambaye wuguhanwa"
  40,28,"Haca havuga umwe mu bantu baba Isilamu ati:- nawe akaba yari mu bantu bo kwa Fir’auni yanyegeza ubu Isilamu bwiwe ati:- Yoh! Mbega mugomba mwice umuntu ngo n’uko yavuze Umuremyi wanje, n’iyo Mana, mu vy’ukuri uyo muntu yaje kuri mwebwe afise n’ivyemezo biri k’umugaragaro akaba yaje ava ku Muremyi wanyu, rero niyaba ari umubeshi ubwo bubeshi bwiwe buri kuri we wenyene, kandi niyaba ari umunyakuri mwebwe muzoshikirwa na bimwe muri ivyo yabaraganiye, ntankeka rero Imana ntiyigera irongora uwurenga akarimbi, kandi akaba n’umubeshi karuhariwe"
  40,29,"Mwebwe bantu banje, kuri uno musi murafise ubwami kandi murafise n’intsinzi ng’aha kw’Isi, none ni nde azo dufasha nuku turokora n’ibihano vy’Imana bidushikiriye? Fir’auni yishuye avuga ati:- ntakuntu noba hanura atari nkuko jewe ndabibona, canke jewe sindaba rongora atari munzira nziza yabarokotse"
  40,30,"N’umwe muri bamwe bemeye Imana yiwe y’ukuri yagumye avuga ati:- mwa bantu banje mu vy’ukuri jewe ndabatinya nk’akarorero k’umusi w’imirwi y’abansi b’Imana"
  40,31,"Nk’akarorero k’abantu b’intumwa y’Imana Nuhu (iii) hamwe n’abantu b’intumwa y’Imana Aadi (iii) n’intumwa y’Imana Thamuda (iii) hamwe nabaje munyuma yabo, n’Imana, rero Imana ntikunda uwuhemukira abantu bayo"
  40,32,Namwe bantu banje mu vy’ukuri jewe ndabatinyira kuri wa musi wugu hamagarana
  40,33,"Mugihe muzo hindukira inyuma, nta muntu azoba kingira ku Mana izoba ihari, nuwuzo ciribwa urubanza n’Imana yuko ari mu bantu bazimiye, uyo muntu ntawuzo murongora mu bantu uwariwe wese"
  40,34,"Kandi ntankeka kera mwarashikiwe n’intumwa y’Imana Yussufu (iii) ifise n’ivyemezo biri k’umugaragaro, mugabo mwebwe mwabandanije mugira amakenga kuvyo yabashikirije, kugeza aho yasandaba niho mwaciye muvuga muti:- Imana ntizosubira kuzana iyindi ntumwa y’Imana munyuma yiwe, niba ari uko Imana yama ireka umuntu akazimira kuwarenze imbibe zayo no kubera ibicumuro vyuwitera amakenga"
  40,35,"Abaharira kumajambo y’Imana badafise ivyemezo ivyarivyo vyose vyabashikiye, n’ishavuzo rihambaye imbere y’Imana n’imbere yabemeye Imana y’ukuri, uku niko Imana itera ikidodo kumutima yabiha yagiza nukwishima"
  40,36,"Na Fir’auni yavuze ati:- ewe Hamana, nunyubakire ikimenyetso kugira ngo nshobore gushikira inzira"
  40,37,"Inzira yo mw’ijuru kugira ngo mbone Imana ya Mussa (iii), mu vy’ukuri ndamuzi neza yuko ari umubeshi karuhariwe, uko rero niko Fir’auni yasharijwe kumabi y’ibikorwa vyiwe nukuzitirirwa inzira mugabo ingeso za Fir’auni ntizabaye atari uguhonywa kwiwe gusa"
  40,38,"Numwe yemera yabandanije avuga ati:- bantu banje nimu nkurikire jewe nzoba rongora munzira y’ihumure"
  40,39,"Mwebwe bantu banje, mu vy’ukuri ubu buzima bwo kuri iy’Isi n’umunezero gusa, kandi ntankeka niyo mw’Ijuru niyo nzu yukuba mwo burundu"
  40,40,"Umugizi w’inabi ntaco azorihwa atari ibikwiranye n’amabi yiwe, n’uwugira ineza haba k’umugabo canke k’umugore nawe ari umu Isilamu, rero abo bantu bazo kwinjizwa mw’Ijuru baze bahabwe muri ayo majuru batarinze kugirirwa ibiharuro"
  40,41,"Namwe bantu banje, ni kuki jewe ndaba hamagarira k’uburokoke namwe muka mpamagarira mumuriro udahera"
  40,42,"Mumpamagaye ngo mpakane Imana nukuyi gereranya nuwo ntazi, nanje ndaba hamagarira k’uwufise ubushobozi kandi ariwe nyene imbabazi zihagije"
  40,43,"Ntankeka mwebwe mumpamagaye ngo ngende gusenga abadafise ubutumwa bwo ng’aha kw’Isi canke ubutumwa canke ubwo mw’Ijuru n’ingaruka yatwese ni ku Mana, nabarenga imbibe z’Imana abo nibo bantu bo mumuriro udahera"
  40,44,"Ubu vuba muzoyibuka kuvyo nababwiye, nanje ndabikesheje Imana ivyanje vyose, mu vy’ukuri irababona abantu biwe bose"
  40,45,Hanyuma Imana yaramukingiye n’amabi y’ingeso zabo bagize hamwe n’ibihano bibi vyabakikuje abo bantu bokwa Fir’auni nawe arimwo
  40,46,"Ibihano vyo mumuriro udahera bizo kwerekanwa mugitondo no kumugoroba no kuri uwo musi niho hazobonekera umusi w’imperuka haze hazovurwe hati:- nimu binjize abo bantu ba Fir’auni mubihano bikaze cane"
  40,47,"Nibagira ibihari muri uwo muriro udahera mugihe abati shoboye bazoba bwira abamye bishima bati:- mu vy’ukuri twebwe twari mumurwi wanyu, mbega mwoshobora kudukurira igice gitoyi c’uwo muriro udahera"
  40,48,"Bazovuga bamwe bahora bishima bati:- twese dukoraniye ng’aha Imana iramaze kuducira urubanza ruri hagati y’ibiremwa vyiwe"
  40,49,"Nabazoba bari mumuriro udahera bazobwira abacungereye umuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu bati :- nimusabe Umuremyi wanyu atugabanirize umusi umwe w’ibi bihano"
  40,50,"Bazobishura bati:- mbega ntimwamye mushikirwa n’intumwa z’Imana zanyu zifise ivyemezo biri k’umugaragaro, nabo bazobishura bati:- nukubera iki? nabo bazo babwira bati:- nimusabe n’ibisabisho vy’abatemera Imana yabo y’ukuri ntibibaho atari ubuzimire bw’impfagusa"
  40,51,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe dukingira intumwa z’Imana zacu hamwe n’abemeye mubuzima bwo ng’aha kw’Isi n’igihe hazohagarara ivyabona bizo kwemeza ibikorwa vy’ibiremwa vyose
  40,52,"N’umusi utazo fasha abahemukiye imitima yabo kuvyitwazo vyabo kandi bakazoronka n’umuvumo w’Imana, n’ubwicaro bwabo buzoba ari bubi cane"
  40,53,Mu vy’ukuri twarahaye intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) uburongozi dutako tubaha n’ibisigi bene Israeri igitabu c’Imana
  40,54,Uburongozi hamwe n’icibutso ku bantu bafise ubwenge
  40,55,"Rero nimu tenyenye ntankeka indagano z’Imana ni z’ukuri na wewe nusabe ikigongwe kubera ibicumuro vyawe, uteko uhayagize Umuremyi wawe nukuyibuka uko bugorovye no mugitondo"
  40,56,"Mu vy’ukuri bamwe bagira ibihari kumajambo y’Imana matagatifu atavyemezo bafise vyabashikiye ntabiri mumishaha yabo atari ubwishime gusa, mugabo ntaco bazoshikako ahubwo wewe niwikingire ku Muremyi wawe, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo yumva nukubona"
  40,57,"Mu vy’ukuri iremwa ry’Amajuru n’Isi ni rininiya cane gusumba iremwa ry’abantu bose, mugabo abantu benshi ntavyo bazi"
  40,58,"Impumyi hamwe n’uwubona ntibangana, n’abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri nukugira ibikorwa vyiza hamwe nabagira amabi y’amarorerwa mugabo muvyo mwibuka mwebwe bantu n’ibintu bikeyi cane"
  40,59,"Mu vy’ukuri umuhero w’Isi uzoshika kandi ntamakenga arimwo, mugabo abantu benshi ntavyo bemera"
  40,60,"N’Umuremyi wanyu yavuze ati:- nimunsabe ico mwipfuza nanje nzobi shura, mu vy’ukuri barya bishima mukugira amasengesho yanje, ntankeka abo bantu bazokwinjira mumuriro udahera bateterewe"
  40,61,"Imana niyo yabagiriye Ijoro kugira ngo muruhukire mwo, hanyuma ibagirira umutaga urimwo umuco, mu vy’ukuri Imana ningira kamaro kaniniya ku bantu mugabo benshi muribo ntibashima"
  40,62,"Iyo niyo Mana, kandi niyo Muremyi wanyu yaremye ibintu vyose, ntawundi rero asengwa bimwe vy’ukuri atariyo yonyene, none muhindukizwa hehe"
  40,63,Uku niko bahinduwe bamwe bahakana amajambo y’Imana
  40,64,"Imana nirya yabagiriye Isi kuba ari ahantu hanyu hukubaho, n’ijuru naryo kuba ari igisenge, hanyuma ibagirira amashusho meza ariyo mashusho yanyu, itako ibaha n’ibintu vyiza, iyo niyo Mana Muremyi wanyu, rero uwufise iyi migisha yose n’Imana Umuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose"
  40,65,"Imana niyo ifise ubuzima bw’imisi yose, ntawundi asengwa bimwe vy’ukuri atariyo yonyene gusa, rero nimu yisabe bimwe bivuye kumishaha yanyu kandi muyi kengurukire kuko ishimagizwa ryose niryo rikwiriye Imana Umuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose"
  40,66,"Vuga uti:- jewe narabujijwe gusenga abo musenga mwebwe, mugaca mureka gusenga Imana yanyu y’ukuri, mugihe nashikirwa n’ivyemezo biri k’umugaragaro bivuye ku Muremyi wanje, kandi nkaba narategetswe ku gamburukira Umuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose"
  40,67,"Niyo yabaremye ibakuye mw’ivu hanyuma mw’Ima ry’intanga hanyuma ibakura mukimanyu c’amaraso hanyuma ibakura mubwana bw’uruhinja mukiri batoyi kugira ngo mushike mubigero vyukuronka inguvu zanyu zikwiye, hanyuma mushike mubusaza, n’abandi muri mwebwe bitaba Umuremyi wabo imbere yugushika mubusaza bwabo, kugira ngo mushikire kuri ico kiringo cagenywe no kugira ngo mube mufise ubwenge"
  40,68,"Niyo irema kandi niyo yica, rero mugihe iciriye urubanza rw’ikintu ikibwira iti nikibe kigaca kiba isase"
  40,69,Mbega ntimubona bamwe baharira kumajambo y’Imana bamaze kuyemeza none bahindukira hehe
  40,70,Abahakanye igitabu c’Imana hamwe n’ubutumwa twarungikanye intumwa zacu mugabo ubu vuba bazotahura neza
  40,71,Mugihe imvutu zizoba ziri mubunigo bwabo n’iminyororo iri kumaguru yabo nabo bakwegwa
  40,72,Mumazi y’amarike hanyuma baturirwe mu mukomezwa
  40,73,"Hanyuma baze babwirwe bati:- bari hehe bamwe mwahora mugereranya Imana n’izindi Mana"
  40,74,"Atari Imana y’ukuri? Hanyuma baze bavuge bati:- baratuzimije, kandi kuva kera narindi ntitwahora dusenga uwariwe wese, uku rero niko Imana ireka abo batayemera bimwe vy’ukuri kugira ngo batakare baje kure"
  40,75,Ibi vyose nukubera yuko mwamye mwishima kuri iy’Isi atakuri mubifitiye kandi kubera yuko mwamye mwishima
  40,76,"Nimwinjire munzugi z’uwo muriro witiriwe Jahannamu mubeyo mubuzima bwanyu bwose, mbega n’amabi ameze gute y’ubwo bwicaro bw’abantu bishima"
  40,77,"Rero nurindire, mu vy’ukuri indagano y’Imana ni y’ukuri, nitwa kwereka muri bimwe twakwemereye canke nitwakwica nabo bazosubizwa iwacu"
  40,78,"Mu vy’ukuri twararungitse intumwa z’Imana imbere yawe, abandi muribo twarabakubwiye n’abandi nabo ntabo twakubwiye, rero ntivyari kuba ngombwa kuntumwa y’Imana iyariyo yose ngo izane ibitangaro atari kw’itegeko ry’Imana, no mugihe hazoshika itegeko ry’Imana hazotegekwa ukuri kwama nabagira ibitari mumategeko bazoronswa uruhombo kuri uwo mwanya"
  40,79,Imana nirya yabagiriye ibikoko kugira ngo muvyurire ko bimwe murivyo n’ibindi navyo muvyikenure ko
  40,80,No muri ivyo bikoko nyene harimwo ibibafitiye akamaro mukuronkera mwo ivyo mwipfuza mwo vyose bivuye mubikiriza vyanyu hamwe nugutwarwa hejuru yavyo no kumato
  40,81,"Nayo niyo ibereka ibimenyetso vyayo, none mwebwe muhakana iki mumigisha y’Imana"
  40,82,Mbega ntibagize urugendo kuri iy’Isi nukuraba uko vyabaye mumpera zabamwe bamyeho imbere yabo? Bari benshi cane gubasumba no mubushobozi bwabo no kunyubakwa zabo zo ng’aha kw’Isi kuri ivyo vyose ntaco vyabamariye muri ivyo bahora bagira
  40,83,Rero mugihe bashikirwa n’intumwa z’Imana zo muribo zifise n’ivyemezo biri k’umugaragaro baranezerejwe n’ubumenyi bari basanganywe baca bakikuzwa nivyo bahora bafata minenerwe
  40,84,"Mugihe babona ibihano vyacu baciye bavuga bati:- turemeye Imana yuko ariyo yonyene rudende, kandi turahakanye kuvyo twahora tugereranya nayo"
  40,85,"Mugabo ukwemera kwabo ntaco vyabamariye mugihe bari bamaze kubona ibihano vyacu, rero n’ibisanzwe ku Mana kuvyabaye ku bantu bayo, nayo abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri bazoronka uruhombo runiniya"
  41,1,"Ha, Miiym. (Insiguro yizi ndome hamwe n’uwufise ubumenyi bwazo zose n’Imana yonyene gusa)"
  41,2,Iri manurwa nirivuye ku Mana nyene imigisha myinshi na nyene imigisha mito mito
  41,3,Iki gitabu gitandukanya amajambo yaco nugu somwa mururimi rw ’icarabu kubantu bafise ubumenyi
  41,4,"Gitomora inkuru nziza hamwe nugutuza, mugabo benshi muribo barahakanye ari naco gituma batumva"
  41,5,"Nabo bavuze bati:- imitima yacu iri mumi pfundikizo kuvyo uduhamagarira, no mumatwi yacu harimwo uburemere, no hagati yacu na wewe hariho uruzitiro, none nugire ivyawe natwe twigirire ivyacu"
  41,6,"Vuga uti:- ntankeka jewe ndi umuntu nkamwe nshikirizwa ubutumwa yuko Imana yanyu ari Imana imwe rudende rero nimu yizere, kandi muyisabe n’ikigongwe, n’ibihano vyayo bizoshikira kuri bamwe bayigereranya n’ibindi bintu"
  41,7,"Nabada tanga imperezwa z’amatungo yabo, bagahakana n’umusi w’umuhero w’Isi yuko utazobaho"
  41,8,"Nayo abemera Imana yabo y’ukuri nukugira ibikorwa vyiza, kuribo izoba ariyo mpembo idahera"
  41,9,"Vuga uti:- Mbega si mwebwe muhakana uwaremye Isi mumisi ibiri gusa mugaca muyiha abagereranyi bw’ibindi bintu? Uyu niwe muremyi w’ibiremwa vyose"
  41,10,"Nayo niyo yashize ho imisozi hejuru y’Isi, nuguhezagira ibiri muriyo nuku gereranya muriyo ibifungurwa vyayo kumisi ine, ivyo n’ivyukuri ku bantu babaza"
  41,11,"Hanyuma atumbera amajuru nayo yari imyotsi aca abwira Amajuru n’Isi ati:- nimuze mwanka mushaka, vyose vyishura biti:- twaje n’ubu gamburutsi buhagije"
  41,12,"Hanyuma ica igira Amajuru yose uko ari indwi mumisi ibiri n’Ijuru rimwe rica rishingwa ibikorwa ryavyo, hanyuma twarasharije iri juru riri hafi yanyu n’amatara, hamwe nukurikingira, urwo nirwo rugero rw’Imana nyene ubumenyi"
  41,13,"Rero nibatavyitaho, wewe nuvuge uti:- Jewe ndabatujije n’ibihano bimeze nk’ibihano vyo kwa bene Aadi na Thamudu"
  41,14,"Mugihe bashikirwa n’intumwa z’Imana zari imbere yabo n’inyuma yabo zibabwira ziti:- ntimu senge icarico cose atari Imana yonyene gusa, baca bishura bati:- iyo ishaka Umuremyi wacu ntankeka yari kumanura Abamarayika, mu vy’ukuri twebwe turahakanye twivuye inyuma nivyo mwarungikanywe navyo"
  41,15,"Rero abo bantu bokwa Aadi, barishima cane kuri iy’Isi atakuri babifitiye nukuvuga bati:- ni nde afise ubushobozi gusumba twebwe, mbega ntibabonye yuko Imana yabaremye ifise ubushobozi kubasumvya, nabo bakaguma bahakana amajambo yacu"
  41,16,"Rero twabarungikiye igihuhusi mumisi y’ishari kugira ngo tubahonjeshe ibihano biba tetereza mubuzima bwabo bwo ng’aha kw’Isi, ntankeka ibihano vyo k’umusi w’imperuka nivyo kuba tetereza cane nabo ntibazo rokoka"
  41,17,Na bene Thamudu twaraba rongoye mugabo bakunze ubuhumyi gusumba uburokoke rero umucanwa w’ibihano niwo wasokoye imitima yabo kandi ubatetereza kubera ivyo bahora basoroma
  41,18,Duca turokora abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri nabahora bikingira
  41,19,"N’umusi bazo kwegeranywa abansi b’Imana mumuriro udahera bagashirwa kuruhande, bari mumirwi n’iyindi"
  41,20,"Kugeza aho bazokwegera uwo muriro udahera, niho amatwi yabo, n’amaso yabo, hamwe n’urukoba rw’imibiri yabo, arivyo bizoba ivyabona kuribo kubijanye nivyo bahora bagira"
  41,21,"Nabo bace babwira imibiri yabo iti:- mbega ni kuki mwatubereye ivyabona? Nayo yamibiri ize yishure iti:- Imana niyo yavugishije ibintu vyose ari nayo yatuvugishije, nayo niyo yabaremye ubwambere, n’iwe niyo muzo subirayo"
  41,22,"Ntimwa hora mucinyegeza kugeza naho amatwi yanyu n’amaso yanyu hamwe n’imibiri yanyu itabaye igitanga ivyabona kuri mwebwe, ahubwo mwiketse yuko Imana itazi ibintu vyinshi muvyo mwahora mugira"
  41,23,Rero uko kwikeka kwanyu mwamye mwikeka Umuremyi wanyu niho yabahoneje nukuba mu bantu bari muruhombo
  41,24,"Nibihangana kuri uwo mukomezwa aribwo bwicaro bwabo, nayo niba bazotanga impamvu bakaba bari mubazo kwemererwa izo mvo zabo"
  41,25,"Twaraba shiriyeho abagenzi babasharijije kubiri imbere yabo n’inyuma yabo, mugabo haca hemezwa ijambo bari kumwe n’amakungu yabayeho imbere yabo hakaba harimwo ibisigo n’abantu, mu vy’ukuri baciye baba mu bantu bari muruhombo"
  41,26,"Baravuze abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri bati:- ntimwumvirize iyi Qur’aani, kandi muyikomere n’induru nyinshi nkumbure mworonka intsinzi"
  41,27,Rero abo bahakanyi b’Imana yabo y’ukuri tuzoba honjesha ibihano bikaze cane hanyuma tuze tubarihe impembo mbi cane ijanye nivyo bahora bagira
  41,28,Iyo niyo mpembo y’abansi b’Imana kuko umuriro udahera nibwo bwicaro bwabo kandi niyo mpembo yabo kubera yuko bamye bahakana amajambo yacu matagatifu
  41,29,"Na bamwe bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri bazovuga bati:- Muremyi wacu, nutwereke bamwe batuzimiza haba mubisigo n’abantu kugira ngo tubashire hasi y’amaguru yacu kandi babe mu bantu bari hasi cane"
  41,30,"Abavuze yuko Umuremyi wacu ngo n’Imana, hanyuma bagaca bagira inyifato nziza, abo bantu nibo bamanukirwa n’Abamarayika, mugihe cugusohoka umitima yabo nukubabwira bati ntimugire ubwoba, kandi ntimu maramare ahubwo nimu nezerwe kubera Ijuru mwari mwaraganiwe n’Imana yanyu"
  41,31,"Twebwe turi abakunzi banyu kubijanye n’ubuzima bwo ng’aha kw’Isi nubwo mw’Ijuru, niyo mw’Ijuru muzo haronkera yo ivyo mwipfuza yo vyose n’imititima yanyu, niyo mw’ijuru muzo haronkera yo ivyo mwipfuza mwo vyose"
  41,32,N’inzimano ivuye ku Muremyi wanyu ariyo nyene ikigongwe n’impuhwe zihagije
  41,33,"Ni nde avuga imvugo nziza gusumba uwu hamagara ibiremwa vy’Imana nukugira ibikorwa vyiza nukuvuga iti:- mu vy’ukuri jewe ndi muba Isilamu"
  41,34,"Ibintu vyiza hamwe n’ibintu bibi ntibiba kimwe, nukureho amabi ugirirwa kumeza, uzoca wisanga n’umwe ari hagati hagati yawe n’uwuri hagati yiwe harimwo urwanko ruzoba nk’incuti yawe bufitaniye umubabaro mwinshi cane"
  41,35,Mugabo ntibazo habwa atari mubigumije kandi ntibazo habwa atari bamwe bafise iteka rininiya
  41,36,"Niyaba Shetani yaraba henze kubera ubuhinga bwayo ikoresha, wewe ni wirinde ku Muna kuko ariyo yumva kandi ariyo ifise ubumemyi"
  41,37,"No mubimenyetso vyayo, n’Ijoro n’Umutaga hamwe n’Izuba n’Ukwezi, ntimuri pfukamire nugushira imitwe yanyu hasi ngo muriko mura senga iryo Zuba canke Ukwezi ahubwo ni musenge Imana yabiremye ni mwaba muyisenga"
  41,38,"Nibagira amanyama Imana ntibakeneye kuko n’ibiremwa vyeranda bari ku Muremyi wawe, nabo bayi hayagiza Ijoro n’Umutaga bata ruhuka"
  41,39,"No mubimenyetso vyayo nuko ubona Isi ihoyahoya mugabo mugihe tuyimanuriyeko amazi, uca uyibona itotahaye ntankeka uwasubiye kuyiha ubuzima niyo izosubira kuzura abapfuye mu vy’ukuri niyo ifise ubushobozi buri hejuru y’ibintu vyose"
  41,40,"Mu vy’ukuri abahengamiye munzira itari iy’ukuri kumajambo yacu ntaco batunyegeza ko, mbega uwuzotabwa mumuriro udahera niwe muntu mwiza gusumba canke uwuzoza afise amahoro kuri uwo musi w’imperuka, rero nimugire ivyo mwishakiye mu vy’ukuri niyo ibona ivyo mugira vyose"
  41,41,"Mu vy’ukuri bamwe bahakana ubutumwa bw’Imana mugihe bubashikiye, ntankeka ico n’igitabu gisonerwa"
  41,42,Ntabubeshi buzo gishikira imbere yaco canke inyuma yaco kuko camanuwe na nyene ubuhizi aninahazwa cane
  41,43,Ntubwirwa atari yamajambo nyene babwiwe intumwa z’Imana zaho hambere yawe mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe ni nyene imbabazi kandi ni nyene ibihano bibabaza
  41,44,"Mbega iyo tugira iyi Qur’aani ntagatifu ngo ibe mururimi rw’icarabu abantu bari kuvuga bati:- ni kuki aya majambo y’iki gitabu adasobanuwe neza? Rero ururimi rutari urw’icarabu, n’intumwa y’Imana ikaba yari umwarabu, wewe nuvuge uti:- aya majambo y’Imana matagatifu n’uburongozi n’impemburo kuba cemeye nayo bamwe bata cemeye harimwo uburemere buri mumatwi yabo, niyo Qur’aani ntagatifu n’umwijima kuribo, abo nibo bitwa mugihe bari kure cane"
  41,45,"Mu vy’ukuri twarahaye intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) igitabu c’Imana mugabo haciye haba uku tumvikana kwaco nayo iyo hataba imvugo yatangujwe ivuye ku Muremyi wawe yuko urwo rubanza ari urubanza rwo mw’Ijuru, bari kuruciribwa ubu vuba na bwango, kandi nabo barafise amakenga abashira mwo impungenge y’ibi vyose vyazananye n’intumwa y’Imana Muhammadi (aui)"
  41,46,"Uwugira ineza iyariyo yose ayigirira umutima wiwe, n’uwugira inabi nawe ayigira umutima wiwe kubwiwe, n’Umuremyi wawe ntahemukira abantu bayo beranda"
  41,47,"Ubumenyi bwukumenya umusi w’umuhero w’Isi usubizwa ku Mana yonyene, n’ivyamwa ntibiva mubishishwa vyavyo canke umukenyezi ntasama imbanyi yiwe canke ashike aho yibaruka atari kubumenyi bw’Imana, n’umusi Imana izoba hamagara izovuga iti:- bari hehe basoma mbike banje? Nabo bazo kwishura bati:- turemeye bimwe bivuye kumitima yacu yuko ata n’umwe muri twebwe ari muvy’abona"
  41,48,Nabamwe bahora babasenga aho hambere hahise ubu barazi manganye kandi bakaba bariyemeje yuko ata buhungiro bafise
  41,49,"Umuntu ntaruhuka mugusaba ibisabisho vy’amahoro, mugihe ahuye n’ivyago, kuko mumwanya aca yihebura nukutagira icizero icarico cose"
  41,50,"Tumu honjesheje imigisha yacu munyuma y’ingorane zamushikiye mumwanya aca avuga ati:- ibi vyose birankwiye jewe kandi sinizeye yuko umuhero w’Isi uzoboneka kandi ninasubizwa ku Muremyi wanje, ntankeka ndafise ivyiza vyanje kuriyo, rero natwe tuzoba menyesha abo bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri kuri ivyo bagize kandi tuba honjeshe ibihano bikomeye cane"
  41,51,"Mugihe duhaye umuntu imigisha yacu aca ahinduka nukuja kurundi ruhande, mugabo ahuye n’ivyago mumwanya aca ahinduka nukugira ibisabisho birebire"
  41,52,"Vuga uti:- mubibona gute niyaba aya majambo avuye ku Mana hanyuma mwebwe mukaya hakana, none yoba ari nde yazimiye gusumba urya ari mubihari vyakure"
  41,53,"Tuzobereka aya majambo yacu no mubihugu vyakure hamwe no kumitima yabo bonyene kugeza aho bazomenyekana yuko ari ivy’ukuri, mbega ntibihagije yuko Umuremyi wawe ariyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ibintu vyose"
  41,54,"Muragabe rero, barafise amakenga yukuzohura n’Umuremyi wabo, mu vy’ukuri niyo ikikuje ibintu vyose"
  42,1,"Haa, Miiym"
  42,2,"Aayin, Siiyn, Qaaf. (Insiguro y’izi ndome hamwe nuwufise ubumenyi bwazo zose n’Imana yonyene gusa)"
  42,3,Uku niko Imana nyene ubushobozi n’ubuhizi ikuzanira ubu butumwa kuri wewe hamwe n’abandi bari imbere yawe
  42,4,"Nivyiwe ibiri Mumajuru no kw’Isi, nayo niyo iri hejuru y’ibintu vyose kandi niyo nkuru"
  42,5,"Amajuru nayo aregereje gusatagurika hejuru yabo n’Abamarayika nibo bahayagiza Umuremyi wabo nukuyi kengurukira nugusabira ikigongwe abari kw’Isi, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo nyene ikigongwe cinshi hamwe n’Imbabazi zihagije"
  42,6,"Nayo abafashe izindi Mana atari Imana y’ukuri ibabikiye kuvyo bagize vyose, na wewe ntujejwe kubika ibikorwa vyabo"
  42,7,"Uku rero niko twakwugururiye iki gitabu c’Imana gitagatifu ca Qur’aani kiri mururimi rw’icarabu kugira ngo utuze abantu bo mugisagara c’iMakkat nabari kumbibe zaco, kandi ubagabishe k’umusi w’ikoraniro ariwo musi udafise amakenga, kuko umurwi umwe uzoba uri mw’Ijuru n’uwundi nawo uzoba uri mumuriro udahera"
  42,8,"Iyo Imana ibishaka yari kubagira abantu bose kuba ari umurwi umwe, mugabo yinjiza mumi hezagiro yayo uwo yishakiye, nayo abahemukiye imitima yabo ntawuzoba kingira canke umufasha"
  42,9,"Yoh ! bafashe izindi Mana aho gufata Imana y’ukuri, mugabo uwuba kingira bimwe vy’ukuri n’Imana, kandi niyo izozura abapfuye, kandi nayo niyo nyene ubushobozi buri hejuru y’ibintu vyose"
  42,10,"Nimu tumvikana kw’ijambo iryariryo ryose, intahe yaryo iri ku Mana, kuko iyo Mana niyo Muremyi wanje nizera kandi iwe niho nzosubira yo"
  42,11,"Umuremyi w’Amajuru n’Isi niwe yabaremeye abakenyezi nkuko mumeze, n’ibikoko navyo ibiremera imvyeyi nuku bongereza muri ubu bwoko n’ubundi rero ntakindi kiriho nkico nayo ikaba ariyo yumva nukubona"
  42,12,"Impfunguruzo z’Amajuru n’Isi zifatiwe mubiganza vyayo vyeranda, yugururira imigisha yayo kuwo yishakiye nukwima kuwo yishakiye, ntankeka rero niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ibintu vyose"
  42,13,"Yarabahaye intahe y’ukuri y’idini nkakurya nyene yasigiye iragi intumwa y’Imana Nuhu (iii) hamwe nivyo twayugururiye, hamwe nivyo twaragiye intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii) hamwe n’intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii)hamwe n’intumwa y’Imana Issa mwene Mariyamu (iii) yuko bohagarika idini ry’Imana, kandi ntimuze mucanemwo kuri ivyo kuko bizobagora kubegeranya kuvyo uba hamagarira, rero Imana niyo yitorera uwo yishakiye nukumu rongora uwayitu mbereye"
  42,14,"Ntiba tandukanye atari munyuma yaho bashikirwa n’ubumenyi kubera ukwinubana kwari hagati yabo, rero iyo ritaba ijambo ryabanje kuba rivuye ku Muremyi wawe kugeza kugihe catege kanijwe kuba, itegeko ryari gusohorwa, mu vy’ukuri bamwe basigiwe ibisigi vy’igitabu munyuma yabo bari bagifitiye amakenga c’ukugene bihindaguzwa hirya no hino"
  42,15,"Nuba hamagare bagende kugira ibi vyose, na wewe ugororoke nkuko wategetswe, kandi ntukurikire ivyipfuzo vyabo kandi uvuge uti:- jewe ndemeye ibitabu vyose vyamanuwe n’Imana kandi nategetswe kuba umunyakuri hagati yanyu, Imana nayo niyo Muremyi wacu kandi niyo Muremyi wanyu, ibikorwa vyacu tubigira kubera twebwe nyene gusa, n’ibikorwa vyanyu mubigira kubera mwebwe nyene gusa, ntamatati ari hagati yacu na mwebwe n’Imana izo twegeranya hamwe n’ingaruka izoba iri iwe"
  42,16,"Nabahariye kubera idini ry’Imana kandi bamaze kwemererwa, ivyitwazo vyabo ntashingiro bizoba bifise imbere y’Umuremyi wabo no hejuru yabo hazoba hari ishavu, kandi hazoba kuribo ibihano bikaze cane"
  42,17,"Imana niyo yamanuye iki gitabu c’ukuri hamwe n’iminzani, none n’igiki kizo kumenyesha yuko nkumbure umusi w’umuhero w’Isi wegereje kuba"
  42,18,"Abatemera Imana yabo y’ukuri bama bagusaba yuko uwo musi woshika hakiri kare, nayo abemera Imana yabo y’ukuri barawutinya uwo musi kandi barazi neza yuko ari uw’ukuri mu vy’ukuri abo baharira kubijanye n’umuhero w’Isi bari mubuzimire bwakure cane"
  42,19,"Imana rugira vyose n’intungane kubiremwa vyayo, kuko niyo iha imigisha yayo kuwo yishakiye, kandi niyo ifise ubushobozi n’intsinzi nyakuri"
  42,20,"Uwushaka kuronka impembo y’umusi w’imperuka twebwe tuzoyi mwongereza kuri iyo mpembo yiwe yaronse, rero nuwurondera impembo y’aha kw’Isi tuzoyimuha, mugabo iyo mw’ijuru ntana kimwe azoba afise kumigisha y’amahoro"
  42,21,"Yoh! Barafise abo bacuditse nabo b’Imana baba shiriye ho iyindi dini Imana itaba shiriye ho uruhusha, nayo iyo hataba ijambo ryugu tandukanya amategeko rero ayo mategeko yari kuba hagati yabo mu vy’ukuri hazoba kuba hemukiye imitima yabo ibihano bibabaza cane"
  42,22,"Uzobabona abahemukiye imitima yabo ingene bajugumira kubera ivyo bagize kandi ivyo bintu bizoba shikira atagisivya, nayo abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri hamwe nukugira ibikorwa vyiza bazoba bari mumirima myiza iri mw’ijuru, bakazo ronka ivyo bipfuza mwo vyose bivuye ku Muremyi wabo, iyo niyo ngabirano niniya kuribo"
  42,23,"Iyi niyo nkuru nziza Imana yabwiye abantu bayo bayemeye hamwe nukugira ibikorwa vyiza, nawe nuvuge uti:- kuri ibi vyose ntampembo iyariyo yose nsavye kuri mwebwe, mugabo ngomba yuko mwokunda ivyobegereza ku Mana, rero uwuzogira ineza tuzo mwongereza ineza mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo ifise ikigongwe cinshi hamwe nugushimirwa"
  42,24,"Egome baravuze bati:- yabesheye Imana yuko ibishatse yoteye igikumu k’umutima wawe, nayo niyo ifuta ibitari ivy’ukuri, nu kwemeza ivy’ukuri kumajambo yayo atomoye, ntankeka Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ibiri mubikiriza vyanyu"
  42,25,"Nayo niyo yakira ikigongwe c’abantu bayo, nugu hanagurira amakosa nukuba ifise ubumenyi bw’ivyo mugira vyose"
  42,26,"Ni ngombwa kubemera Imana yabo y’ukuri hamwe nukugira ibikorwa vyiza izo bongereza imigisha yayo, nayo abatemera Imana yabo y’ukuri bazoba bari mubihano bikaze cane"
  42,27,"Iyo Imana itanga imigisha yayo myinshi ikayiha abantu bayo beranda, ntankeka abo bantu bo kwishimye cane kuri iy’Isi mugabo iyo migisha iyimanura kurugero yishakiye mu vy’ukuri kubantu bayo beranda irabafitiye inkuru zabo zose nukuba bona"
  42,28,"Nayo niyo imanura imvura mugihe abantu bamaze kwihebura, nayo igaca ikwiza imigisha yayo, nayo niyo ikingira ibintu vyose nugu shimirwa"
  42,29,No mubimenyetso vyayo nuku kuremwa kw’Amajuru n’Isi hamwe n’ibi bintu bifise ubuzima yakwiragije hose nayo niyo ifise ubushobozi bukwiye bwuku vyegeranya nkuko ibishaka
  42,30,"N’ivyago bibashikira nukubera ibikorwa vy’amaboko yanyu yakoze, kandi Imana igira ikigongwe kubintu vyinshi"
  42,31,"Namwe ntimushobora kuyinanira ng’aha kw’Isi, kandi ntaco mufise imbere yayo kubijanye n’ukwikingira canke kubijanye n’abafasha"
  42,32,No mubimenyetso vyayo hamwe n’amato ari mubiyaga ameze nk’Imisozi
  42,33,"Ibishatse irahagarika imiyaga hanyuma ayo mato agaca ahagarara neza atankomanzi hejuru yayo mazi, mu vy’ukuri muri ibi vyose harimwo ibimenyetso vy’uwutenyenya n’ugushima cane"
  42,34,Canke yoyahonya kubera ivyo bakoze kandi nukugirira ikigongwe kubintu vyinshi cane
  42,35,Bazomenya bamwe bagira ibihari vy’amajambo yacu kuko atamahungiro bafise yugu hungira mwo
  42,36,"Ibi vyose mwahawe nivyu kwinezereza kubuzima bwo ngaha kw’Isi gusa, mugabo ibiri ku Mana nivyo vyiza gusumba, kandi nivyo biramba, rero bizoba bibakwiye abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri hamwe n’ukwizera Umuremyi wabo"
  42,37,Nabishize kure y’ibicumuro bininiya hamwe n’ibintu bibi hamwe n’abantu mugihe bashavuye baca bagira ikigongwe
  42,38,Nabitavye akamo ku Muremyi wabo nugu hagarika amasengesho yabo hamwe nugu hanurana mubintu vyabo kandi bagatanga muvyo twabahaye
  42,39,Na bamwe ubwishime bwabo mugihe bwabafashe baca birwanira kumitima yabo
  42,40,"Nayo impembo y’amabi n’amabi angana nayo mabi, mugabo uwugira imbabazi hamwe n’uwuba nguranya mumatati, impembo yiwe iri ku Mana, kandi ntankeka Imana ntikunda abayi hemukira"
  42,41,"Na barya bihorana mugihe bamaze guhemukirwa, abo ntayindi nzira kuribo yugutabwa ko umwikomo"
  42,42,Ahubwo umwikomo uri hejuru yabarya bahemukira abantu nukuba girira igitsure ng’aha kw’Isi atakuri kurimwo abo rero nibo bazoronka ibihano bibabaza cane
  42,43,N’uwutenyenya nukugira ikigongwe ntankeka ivyo ni mubintu bikuru vy’ukugirira ishaka kugira ngo bigirwe
  42,44,"Nuw’Imana yaretse kugira ngo azimire ntawumu kingira munyuma yiwe, uca ubona abahemukiye imitima yabo mugihe bazobona ibihano bazovuga bati:- mbega hari iyindi nzira yukugaruka"
  42,45,"Uzoba bona bajanwa mumuriro udahera nabo baboneka yuko bafise amaganya hamwe n’ibimara mare vyinshi kandi barabana kubandi nabo bihishije, nayo abameye Imana yabo y’ukuri bazovuga bati:- mu vy’ukuri abazoronka uruhombo ni muri barya bazoba bafise uruhombo rw’imitima yabo hamwe n’abantu babo, hanyuma kuri uwo musi w’imperuka ntankeka abahemukiye imitima yabo bazoba bari mubihano vyurutavana ko"
  42,46,"Kandi ntabagenzi bazoba bafise bazoba fasha imbere y’Imana, nuwo Imana yashakiye yuko azimira ntayindi nzira ihari kuriwe"
  42,47,"Nimwitabire Umuremyi wanyu imbere yugushika kuri wamusi uda hengeshanya uzoba uvuye ku Mana, kuko kuri uwo musi ntama hungiro yukwirukira ho kandi ntaho muzo kwankira"
  42,48,"Nibatitaho natwe ntitwa kurungitse ngo ube uwubakingira, ivyo ntubijejwe atari uko ubashikiriza ubutumwa gusa, mu vy’ukuri mugihe tumu honjesheje umuntu imigisha ivuye iwacu aca anezerwa cane, rero ashikiwe n’ingorane izarizo zose kubera ivyo amaboko yiwe yagize uca ubona uyo muntu ahakana Imana"
  42,49,Ubwami bw’Amajuru n’Isi nu bw’Imana kuko irema uko yishakiye kandi igaha uwo yishakiye mubibondo vy’abigeme kandi igaha uwo yishakiye mubibondo vy’abahungu
  42,50,"Canke ikabivanga ivyo bibondo vy’abahungu n’abigeme nukubigira ingumba k’umuntu yishakiye, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo nyene ubumenyi n’ubushobozi"
  42,51,"Ntivyari kuba k’umuntu yuko avugana n’Imana atari munzira ashirirwa mumutima wiwe canke inyuma y’uruzitiro kanaka canke ikarungika intumwa yayo nawe agaca amwereka kurugero ico yipfuza kw’itegeko ryiwe, ntankeka niyo iri hejuru n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  42,52,"Uku rero niko twakweretse ubu butumwa kw’itegeko ryacu ntiwari ufise igitabu icarico cose canke ukwemera ukwariko kwose mugabo twagize iki gitabu gitagatifu ca Qur’aani kuba ariwo muco, no kuri uwo muco twebwe turongora uwo twishakiye mu bantu bacu beranda, kandi mu vy’ukuri wewe urongora munzira igororotse"
  42,53,Inzira y’Imana hamwe nibiri mu Majuru no kw’Isi ni rwiwe rero mumenye yuko ibintu vyose vyama bigaruka ku Mana
  43,1,"Ha, Miiym. (Insiguro y’izi ndome hamwe nuwufise ubumenyi bwazo zose n’Imana yonyene gusa)"
  43,2,Ndarahiye kuri iki gitabu gitagatifu kimenyesha neza aya majambo
  43,3,Ntankeka natwe twagize ngo kibe igisomwa co mururimi rw’icarabu kugira ngo mutegere neza
  43,4,Mu vy’ukuri iyi Qur’aani ntagatifu iri mububiko bw’ibitabu vyose vyavuye iwacu kandi n’igitabu catewe iteka n’ubuhizi
  43,5,Mbega natwe tureke kubibutsa kubera yuko mwabaye abantu mwamaze kurengerana kumabi yanyu
  43,6,Mu bantu bakera twebwe twaraba rungikiye intumwa z’Imana nyinshi
  43,7,Ntantumwa y’Imana iyariyo yose atari uko bahora bayigaya nukuyityoza
  43,8,Rero twaraba honeje abari bafise ubushobozi buhanitse gusumba abo baqurayshi hamwe n’uburorero bw’ibihano vyashikiye abantu baho hambere
  43,9,"Ubabajije uti:- mbega ni nde yaremye Amajuru n’Isi? Mu vy’ukuri bakwishura bati :- uwaremye ibi vyose n’uwufise ubushobozi hamwe n’ubumenyi"
  43,10,Uwabagiriye iy’Isi kuba nk’ubusaswa nukugira amayira muriyo nukugira ngo murongore iyo mugomba kuja ahariho hose
  43,11,Nuwamanuye amazi avuye mubicu kurugero no kuri ayo mazi niho twazuye Isi yari yarapfuye nikuri ivyo niko muzozurwa
  43,12,Uwaremye ikigabo n’ikigore mubintu vyose nukubagirira amato hamwe n’ibikoko mwurira ko
  43,13,"Kugira ngo mwicareko neza hejuru y’imigongo yavyo hanyuma mwibuke imigisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mugihe mwicaye neza hejuru yavyo muvuga muti :- nihaninahazwe Imana yatugamburukije ibi vyose kandi ntitwari kwigirira ibi vyose"
  43,14,Ntankeka twebwe tuzo subira ku Muremyi wacu
  43,15,Bamugirira mubantu beranda ahantu bavuga yuko ibi biremwa ari ibibondo vy’Imana mu vy’ukuri umuntu n’umuhakanyi w’imihezagiro iri k’umugaragaro
  43,16,Yitwariye ibibondo vy’abakobwa muvyo yiremeye mukubatorera mwebwe ibibondo vy’abahungu
  43,17,"Umwe muribo mugihe ashikirijwe inkuru y’ivyo yagiriweko akarorero kanyene imigisha, mumaso yiwe haca hirabura cane n’agahinda kenshi"
  43,18,Uwarerewe mubisharizo nawe kubijanye nibihari ntashobora kuvuga k’umugaragaro
  43,19,"Kandi bagira Abamarayika aribo biremwa vy’Imana vyeranda ngo n’abagore bayo, mbega n’ivyabona mukuremwa kwabo? Ukuba kwabo kw’ivyabona kuzo kwandikwa kandi bazobazwa"
  43,20,"Bavuga bati:- iyo ishaka nyene imigisha mininiya ntitwari kubasenga, kuko atabumenyi bafise kuri ibi vyose kandi ntibavuga atari amajambo y’ububeshi bw’ivyo bavuze"
  43,21,Mbega twebwe ntitwabahaye igitabu imbere y’iki ? Nabo bakaba bagifashe nkankama
  43,22,"Ahubwo bavuga bati :- mu vy’ukuri twebwe twasanze abavyeyi bacu kubera imigenzo yabo natwe twaciye dukurikira nkuko bamye bagira"
  43,23,"Kandi ntitwarungitse uwutuza mubisagara ivyarivyo vyose atari uko abatunzi baho bavuze bati:- mu vy’ukuri twebwe twasanze abavyeyi bacu n’imigenzo yabo natwe duca dukurikiza ingeso zabo"
  43,24,"Yavuze ati:- naho ndabazaniye imigenzo yacu ifise uburokoke bwiza gusumba iyo bari basanganywe abo bavyeyi banyu, nabo baciye bavuga bati:- twebwe turanse ubwo butumwa mwarungikanywe"
  43,25,"Rero natwe duca turabihora, mugabo nimurabe ukugene kwabaye amaherezo yabigize abahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri"
  43,26,"N’intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii) mugihe yabwira umuvyeyi wiwe hamwe n’abantu biwe ati:- ntankeka jewe mbanje kuba kure yivyo mwebwe musenga"
  43,27,Dukuye mwo gusa uwandemye mu vy’ukuri niwe azondongora
  43,28,Ninawe yagize iri jambo rizo gumaho muruvyaro rwiwe kugira ngo bagaruke
  43,29,Ahubwo baranezerejwe mugihe bari kumwe n’abavyeyi babo kugeza naho bashikirwa n’ukuri n’intumwa y’Imana irabi garagaza
  43,30,"Mugihe bashikirwa n’ukuri baciye bavuga bati:- ubu n’uburozi kandi mu vy’ukuri twebwe turabu hakanye"
  43,31,"Nabo bavuze bati:- ni kuki iyi Qur’aani itamanuwe k’umuntu mukuru wo muri ibi bisagara vyacu bibiri bikuru bikuru"
  43,32,"Mbega nibo bagabura imigisha y’Umuremyi wawe, twebwe twarabugabuye ubu buzima bwabo ku buzima bwo ng’aha kw’Isi, kandi twarabareruye bamwe muribo tubaha n’iteka rininiya cane gusumba abandi, kuri ivyo rero bamwe muribo bagira abandi kuba ari abakozi babo, n’imigisha y’Umuremyi wawe niyo myiza gusumba ivyo begeranya"
  43,33,"Iyo hataba abantu kuba ari umurwi umwe, ntankeka twari kugira ibisenge vy’inzu z’abantu bahakana nyene imigisha kuba ari iz’umwakaka hamwe n’ingazi burirako"
  43,34,N’inzugi z’inzu zabo hamwe n’ubusaswa bwabo hamwe n’inyegamo z’ukwegamira ko
  43,35,Ahubwo n’inzahabu mugabo ivyo vyose ntaco bimaze atari amahirwe y’ubuzima bwo ng’aha kw’isi gusa nayo k’umusi w’imperuka uri ku Muremyi wawe niyaba yigamburukira
  43,36,Uwuyagirira ubuhumyi amajambo yanyene imigisha tumushirira ho Shetani kuba ariyo mugenzi wiwe
  43,37,Nabo nabazitira inzira y’amahirwe bakiyumvira yuko barokotse
  43,38,"N’igihe azodushikira k’umusi w’umuhero w’Isi nawe atwarwa mumuriro udahera azovuga abwira Shetani ati:- iyo aba ari kure y’ubuseruko n’ubumanuko hagati yanje na wewe, n’ubugenzi bubi bumeze gute"
  43,39,Uno musi nta nakimwe kizoba marira muvyo mwahemukiye imitima yanyu yuko mwebwe muri kumwe mubijanye n’ibihano
  43,40,"Mbega woshobora kwumvisha abatumva, canke woshobora kurongora impumyi hamwe n’abari mubuzimire buri k’umugaragaro"
  43,41,Twebwe nitwagukura ng’aha kw’isi utarabona ibihano vyabo ntugire amakenga twebwe tuzokwihora kuribo
  43,42,"Canke twebwe tuzokwereka neza muvyo twasezeranye nabo, natwe ntankeka turafise ububasha buri hejuru yabo"
  43,43,"Rero nubifate nka nkama kuvyo twaguhaye, kandi ntankeka wewe uri munzira nziza igororotse"
  43,44,"Mu vy’ukuri iki n’icibutso kuri wewe no ku bantu bawe, n’ubu vuba mwese muzobazwa"
  43,45,"Nimugende mubaze intumwa zacu twazanye imbere yawe, mbega twebwe twoba twaragize izindi Mana zisengwa aho gusenga nyene imigisha myinshi ihagije"
  43,46,"Ntankeka twebwe twararungitse intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) ifise amajambo yacu iyajana kwa Fir’auni no kubakuru b’abantu babo nukubabwira iti:- mu vy’ukuri jewe nd’intumwa y’Umuremyi w’abantu bose"
  43,47,"Mugabo mugihe yashika afise ivyemezo vyacu, mu mwanya baciye bazitwenga ntibazemera"
  43,48,Kandi ntitwaberetse icemezo icarico cose atari icemezo cari kininiya gusumba ica mugenzi wiwe nukuba fata kubihano vyacu kugira ngo bagaruke iwacu
  43,49,"Nabo bavuze bati:- wamurozi we ! dusabire ku Muremyi wawe kubijanye naya ndagano yaguhaye mu vy’ukuri tuzoba turi mu bantu barongotse"
  43,50,Rero mugihe twaba kuriraho ivyo bihano mukanya isase twaciye tubona bayahonyanga ko
  43,51,"Nuyo Fir’auni yara menyesheje ku bantu biwe avuga ati:- bantu banje intwaro y’igihugu ca Misiri si rwanje hamwe n’izi nzuzi zica imbere yanje, mbega ntavyo mubona"
  43,52,"Canke jewe ntacomaze gusumba uyu Mussa ajunjagariye ng’aha, kandi adashoboye kuvuga ibintu bitomoye"
  43,53,"Mbega ni kuki atambitswe ibisharizo vy’inzahabu, canke ngo haze abamarayika bari kumwe nawe bamu kurikira"
  43,54,"Yasanze bagaba nukiwe n’ubwenge bamu gamburukira, mugihe bari mu bantu bataye umurongo"
  43,55,"Rero mugihe badu shavuza, twaciye tubihora, duca tubibiza mumazi uko bangana bose"
  43,56,Hanyuma twaciye tubagira kuba akarorero n’ibiganiro ku bantu bazoba baje munyuma yabo
  43,57,No mugihe yaciribwa ko akarorero umwana wa Mariyamu (iii) mumwanya abantu bawe baciye bakoma akaruru
  43,58,"Baca bavuga bati:- mbega Imana zacu nizo nziza gusumba canke niwe, canke ntaco bakubwira atari munzira z’ibihari gusa, ahubwo abo bantu n’abasinzi"
  43,59,Ntiyari intumwa y’Imana ariwe Issa mwene Mariyamu (iii) atari uko yari umushumvyi w’Imana twamanuriye nuku mugira umwe muburorero bwiza kuri bene Israeri
  43,60,Iyo tuba dushaka twari kubagira Abamarayika bari ngaha kw’Isi aho kuba ari mwebwe kuri iy’Isi
  43,61,Mu vy’ukuri n’ikimenyetso c’umusi w’umuhero w’Isi kandi ntimukigirire amakenga kandi nimunkurikire iyi niyo nzira igororotse
  43,62,"Kandi Shetani ntibazitire, ntankeka kuri mwebwe niwe mwansi wanyu, kandi niwe mwansi wanyu aboneka neza k’umugaragaro"
  43,63,"Mugihe intumwa y’Imana Issa mwene Mariamu (iii) yari afise ibimenyetso biri k’umugaragaro yavuze ati :- ndabashikiye mfise ubumenyi kugira ngo ndaba menyeshe bimwe muvyo mutumvikanyeko, rero ni mutinye Imana nanje mungamburukire"
  43,64,"Mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo Muremyi wanje kandi niyo Muremyi wanje n’Umuremyi wanyu, rero ni muyisenge kuko niyo nzira igororotse"
  43,65,Imirwi n’iyindi yaracanye mwo rero bazoshikirwa bamwe bahemukiye imitima yabo muguhonywa n’ibihano vy’umusi ubabaza cane
  43,66,Barindiriye iki atari ugushikirwa n’umusi w’umuhero w’Isi gusa kandi ukazoba shikira giturumbuka nabo aho bari batabizi
  43,67,Abagenzi kuri uwo musi bazoba bari abansi kubandi dukuye mwo b’abagenzi bamye bagamburukira Imana yabo y’ukuri
  43,68,Bantu banje ntabwoba muzoba mufise kuri uwo musi w’imperuka kandi mwebwe ntimuzo teterwa
  43,69,Abemeye amajambo yacu bakaba bari aba Isilamu b’ukuri
  43,70,"Nimwinjire mumirima yo mw’ijuru mwebwe n’imiryango yanyu, iyo niho muzo nezerezwa"
  43,71,Bazohora bacishirizwa amasahani y’inzahabu hamwe n’ibikombe vyabo birimwo ivyo imitima yabo yipfuza hamwe n’ivyo amaso yabo azonezereza namwe iyo mw’Ijuru muzobayo mubuzima bwanyu bwose
  43,72,N’uwu n’umurima mwasigiwe kuvyo mwahora mugira
  43,73,Murahafitiye ivyamwa vyinshi muzo fungurira yo
  43,74,Mu vy’ukuri abahakanyi b’Imana bazoba bicaye mubihano vyo mumuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu
  43,75,"Ntibazo ruhutswa nivyo bihano biri muri uwo muriro udahera, kandi niho bazo kwiheburira yo"
  43,76,"Natwe ntitwaba hemukiye, ahubwo nibo bonyene bahemukiye imitima yabo"
  43,77,"Kandi bazokoma induru bavuga bati:- ewe mwami wacu, uyo Muremyi wawe natwice, nawe ace abishura ati :- ntankeka mwebwe aho muri muzoguma muri uwo muriro nyene"
  43,78,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twarakuzaniye ukuri kwama mugabo benshi muri mwebwe mwamye mukugaya uko kuri kwama
  43,79,"Egome,\tboshobora\tgucishaho\titegeko,\tcanke\tnatwe\tturashobora gucishaho irindi"
  43,80,"Canke\tbikeka\tyuko\ttwebwe\ttutumva\tamabanga\tyabo\thamwe n’ukwongorerana kwabo, oya ! n’intumwa zacu ziri hafi yabo baravyandika"
  43,81,"Vuga uti:- nyene imigisha iyo iba ifise ikibondo nari kuba uwambere mukuyisenga"
  43,82,Umuremyi w’Amujuru n’Isi Umuremyi n’inyegamo yiwe ntagatifu iri kure nivyo bayihayagiza ko
  43,83,Rero nimubareke bagume bayogora nugutamba batarika kugeza naho bazohura n’uwo musi wabo baraganiwe
  43,84,"Niyo isengwa mw’Ijuru no kw’Isi, nayo niyo nyene ubuhizi n’ubumenyi buhagiije"
  43,85,"Niyo iterwa iteka ry’ukuri kuko ariwe mwami w’Amajuru n’Isi hamwe n’ibirimwo vyose nirwiwe, kandi irafise ubumenyi bw’ugushika k’umusi w’umuhero w’Isi, namwe uko muri kwose muzo subizwa iwe"
  43,86,Nabo ntabubasha bafise bw’ugu sabira abo basabira atari Imana yonyene dukuye mwo bamwe bemera uku kuri nukuyimenya
  43,87,"Ubabajije uti;- ni nde yabaremye? Mu vy’ukuri bakwishura bati:- n’Imana, none ni hehe bahindukirizwa"
  43,88,"N’imvugo yiwe n’iyi:- ewe Muremyi wanje, mu vy’ukuri aba n’abantu batemera Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  43,89,Rero nubagirire ikigongwe kandi ubabwire amajambo y’amahoro kuko ubu vuba bazotegera neza
  44,1,"Ha, Miiym. (Insiguro y’izi ndome hamwe n’uwufise ubumenyi bwazo zose n’Imana yonyene gusa)"
  44,2,Ndarahiye kuri iki gitabu gitagatifu kigaragaza kubintu vyose vyipfuzwa
  44,3,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\ttwebwe\ttwamanuye\tiyi\tQur’aani\tntagatifu\tmw’ijoro ryahezagiwe, ntankeka rero twebwe turi mu bantu bagabisha"
  44,4,Muri iri joro niho hagaragazwa ibintu vyose bijanye n’ubuhizi
  44,5,Iwacu niho havuye intahe mu vy’ukuri twebwe turi muba rungikwa
  44,6,"N’umuhezagiro uvuye ku Muremyi wawe, ntankeka niyo yumva kandi niyo ifise ubumenyi buhagije"
  44,7,"N’Umuremyi w’Amajuru n’Isi hamwe nibiri muri ivyo vyose, nimwaba mufise icizero nyakuri"
  44,8,"Ntawundi asengwa bimwe vy’ukuri atari Imana yonyene gusa, niwe arema nukwica, niwe Muremyi wanyu kandi niwe Muremyi w’abavyeyi banyu baho hambere"
  44,9,Mugabo abo bahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri barafise amakenga nugu fyinata gusa
  44,10,Rero nurorere wamusi Amajuru azozana umwotsi ubonerana neza na neza
  44,11,"Uzopfuka abantu baze bavuge bati:- ibi n’ibihano bibabaza"
  44,12,"Muremyi\twacu,\tnudukurire\tibi\tbihano\tmu\tvy’ukuri\ttwebwe\ttuzo kwemera"
  44,13,N’akahe kamaro kukwibuka kwabo mugihe bamaze gushikirwa n’intumwa y’Imana iba garagariza ibintu vyose
  44,14,"Baciye\tbabaha\tibitugu\tbavuga\tbati:-\tuyu\tmuntu\tyarigishijwe,\tkandi n’umusazi"
  44,15,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe tuzokuraho ibihano bikeyi gusa mugabo turazi neza yuko muzo subira mubikorwa vyanyu vy’ububisha bugaritse
  44,16,"Umusi tuzobatera igitero ntamusiga, ntankeka twebwe turi\tabahanyi bimwe vy’akarorero"
  44,17,Mu vy’ukuri imbere yabo twebwe twara bagiriye ibibazo abantu bo kwa Fir’auni mugihe bashikirwa n’intumwa y’Imana y’iteka
  44,18,"Ni\tmumpe\tabantu\tberanda\tb’Imana,\tmu\tvy’ukuri\tjewe\tnd’intumwa y’Imana yizigirwa"
  44,19,Kandi ntimwishime cane imbere y’Imana jewe mu vy’ukuri nzobazanira ivyemezo biri k’umugaragaro
  44,20,"Nanje\tnikinze\tk’Umuremyi\twanje\tno\tk’Umuremyi\twanyu\tkugira\tngo ntimu njugunyire ko iminana"
  44,21,Nimwaba muta nyemera nimube kure yanje
  44,22,Niho yasaba Umuremyi wiwe yuko ari abantu babi cane
  44,23,"Rero\tnugende\thamwe\tn’abantu\tbanje\tberanda\tmw’ijoro\tkuko\tmu vy’ukuri mwebwe muzo kurikiranwa atagisivya"
  44,24,Nureke ico kiyaga mu vy’ukuri izo n’ingabo tuzokwibizwa
  44,25,N‘imirima ingahe hamwe n’amasoko angana gute basize
  44,26,N’ibiterwa hamwe n’ahantu heza
  44,27,N’imigisha mininiya bamye binezereza ko
  44,28,Uku rero niko twabahaye ibisigi abandi bantu nk’abo
  44,29,"Amajuru n’Isi ntiyarize kuribo, kandi ntibahawe n’umwanya na mutoyi"
  44,30,Kandi ntankeka twarabarokoye bene Israeri kubihano vy’ukuba tetereza
  44,31,Bivuye kwa Fir’auni mu vy’ukuri niwe yari afise amanyama gusumba abimonogoje mukurenga akarimbi kagenywe n’Imana
  44,32,Duca dutora mwo kubera ubumenyi bwacu gusumba abandi bantu
  44,33,Tubaha mubintu vyacu murivyo harimwo imigisha mininiya kandi iri k’umugaragaro
  44,34,"Mu vy’ukuri aba bahakanyi b’Imana yabo y’ukuri, bavuga bati"
  44,35,"Ntarupfu\trwamyeho\tatari\trwarupfu\trwacu\trwambere,\tkandi\ttwebwe ntituzozurwa"
  44,36,"Rero nimu tugarurire abavyeyi bacu basandavye kuva kera\tnimwaba muvugisha ukuri"
  44,37,"Mbega nibo beza canke abantu bo kwa Tubba’a hamwe n’abari imbere yabo, mu vy’ukuri twebwe twaraba honeje kuko bari mu bantu babi cane"
  44,38,Ntitwaremye Amajuru n’Isi hamwe n’ibirimwo vyose ngo n’ugufyinata
  44,39,"Ntitwabiremye atari uko ari ivy’ukuri, mugabo benshi muribo ntavyo bazi"
  44,40,Mu vy’ukuri umusi w’intahe rukokoma y’ukuri n’umwanya wagenywe kuri bose
  44,41,"Umusi\twaho\tincuti\titazofasha\tmugenziwe\tkukintu\ticarico\tcose\tkandi ntibazorokoka"
  44,42,Dukuyemwo abo Imana izoba yahezagiye kuko ariyo ifise ubushobozi n’imigisha ihagije
  44,43,Ntankeka hari igiti citiriwe Zaqquum
  44,44,N’igifungura abahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri
  44,45,Ni nk’umujumpu washuhijwe ubirira munda zabo
  44,46,Ukabira nk’amazi y’amarike
  44,47,Nimu mufate kandi mumute mu muriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu
  44,48,Hanyuma mumusukire hejuru y’umutwe wiwe y’amazi ashushe y’amarike ahonje ibihano vyayo mazi
  44,49,"Nuhonje, wari mubabtu b’inguvu kandi bafise n’iteka"
  44,50,Mu vy’ukuri ibi nivya bihano mwahora muharira ko
  44,51,Ntankeka bamwe batinya Imana yabo y’ukuri bazoba bari mubibanza vy’amahoro
  44,52,Bazoba bari mumirima irimwo n’amasoko y’amazi
  44,53,Bazo kwambara impuzu zihwahutse nizi remereye kandi barabana
  44,54,Uku niko tuzoha abo bazo kwubakana nabo iyo mw’ijuru
  44,55,Bazoba iyo mw’ijuru baronka ubwoko bwose bw’ivyamwa kandi babeyo mumahoro ntangere
  44,56,"Iyo\tmw’ijuru\tntibazo\thonjerayo\turupfu\tatari\trwarupfu\trwambere, n’Imana izobakingira n’ibihano vyo muriro witiriwe Jahannamu"
  44,57,"Kumihezagiro izoba ivuye ku Muremyi wawe\tiyo niyo izoba ari itsinzi ikomeye cane"
  44,58,Rero twebwe twayoroheje cane iyi Qur’aani ntagatifu kururimi rwawe kugira ngo abantu bibuke
  44,59,Nurindire gusa nabone aho bari bararindiriye
  45,1,"Ha, Miiym. (Insiguro y’izi ndome hamwe n’uwufise ubumenyi bwazo zose n’Imana yonyene gusa)"
  45,2,Imanurwa ry’iki gitabu ryavuye ku Mana nyene ubushobozi n’ubuhizi
  45,3,Ntankeka mw’Ijuru no kw’Isi hariho ibimenyetso bininiya kubera abantu bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri
  45,4,No mw’ishusho ryanyu no mubiremwa yasanzaje hirya no hino harimwo ibimenyetso biri ku bantu bafise icizero
  45,5,"Nukubisanya kw’Ijoro n’Umutaga hamwe n’Imigisha Imana yamanuye ivuye mubicu hamwe nukuzurwa kw’Isi mugihe yari yarapfuye, no kwihindagurika kw’Imiyaga, harimwo ibimenyetso ku bantu bafise ubwenge"
  45,6,"Aya majambo y’Imana tugusomera na y’ukuri, none n’ibihe biganiro bazo kwemera inyuma y’Imana y’ukuri hamwe n’amjambo yayo"
  45,7,Uguhonywa kw’umuntu kuzo mushikira kuwugira ububeshi afise bw’umurengero bw’ibicumuro
  45,8,"Uwumviriza amajambo y’Imana mugihe ariko arasomwa kuriwe, hanyuma agaca afatira kuvyabujijwe hamwe nu kwishima nkuko atavyo yigeze yumva, rero nimu mubwire inkuru y’ibihano bibabaza"
  45,9,"Mugihe yatahuye ikintu gitoyi mu majambo yacu matagatifu aca agifata minenerwe, abantu nk’abo nibo bazoba bafise ibihano bitetereza"
  45,10,"N’inyuma yabo hariho umuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu, nivyo bagize vyose ntana kimwe kizoba marira canke muba bakingira babafashe aho gufashwa n’Imana nabo bazoronka ibihano bininiya cane"
  45,11,"Ubu n’uburokoke, na bamwe bahakanye amajambo y’Umuremyi wabo bazoba bafise ibihano bininiya bizoba bivanye n’ibihano bibabaza cane"
  45,12,"Imana niyo yabaremeye ibiyaga, no murivyo hacamwo amato kw’itegeko ryayo kandi muronderere mwo imigisha yanyu nugu kenguruka kandi mushime"
  45,13,"Niyo yabaremeye ibiri mumajuru no kw’Isi, vyose n’ivyavuye iwe, ntankeka rero muri ibi vyose harimwo ibimenyetso ku bantu biyumvira"
  45,14,Nubwire bamwe bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri babagirire ikigongwe bamwe badatinya imisi y’Imana kugira ngo ibarihe abantu kuvyo bahora bagira
  45,15,"Uwugira ineza iyariyo yose bivana n’umutima wiwe n’uwugira inabi iyariyo yose bivana n’umutima wiwe, hanyuma muzo subizwa ku Muremyi wanyu"
  45,16,"Mu vy’ukuri twarahaye bene Israeri igitabu c’Imana hamwe n’amategeko hamwe n’ubutumwa bw’Imana, dutako tubaha n’ibintu vyiza vyiza hanyuma tubaha n’iteka ntangere gusumba abandi bantu"
  45,17,"Duca tubaha insiguro iri k’umugaragaro hamwe n’amategeko y’Imana, rero ntibigeze bacanamwo atari muyuma y’ugushikirwa n’ubumenyi kubera inzigo yari hagati yabo, mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe azocira urubanza ruzoba hagati yabo k’umusi w’umuhero w’Isi kubijanye nivyo batumvikana ko"
  45,18,"Hanyuma twebwe twagushize hejuru y’ubutungane n’amategeko yacu, rero n’uyakurikize kandi ntukurikire ivyo bipfuza abo bantu atabumenyi bafise"
  45,19,"Mu vy’ukuri abo bantu ntaco bazo kumarira n’ikintu na kimwe imbere y’Imana mu vy’ukuri abahemukiye imitima yabo nibo bagenzi babo kuribo, n’Imana niyo mugenzi wabamwe bayitakambira"
  45,20,"Ibi n’ivyemezo biri k’umugaragaro ku bantu bose, navyo n’uburokoke n’imigisha ku bantu bavyemeza"
  45,21,Mbega biyumvira bamwe bagize amarorerwa y’ibicumuro yuko tuzobagira nkabemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri nukugira ibikorwa vyiza yuko ubuzima bwabo hamwe n’urupfu rwabo bizoba bingana?N’urubanza rubi bazociribwa
  45,22,"N’Imana niyo yaremye Amajuru n’Isi bimwe vy’ukuri kugira ngo umutima w’umuntu uwariwe wese urihwe kubijanye nivyo wakoze, nabo ntibazo hemukirwa"
  45,23,"Mbega wamubonye umwe yagira ivyo yishakiye kubwiwe yuko ariwe Mana yiwe n’Imana ica imureka uko nyene ngo azimire hamwe nuko afise ubumenyi, mugabo Imana ica itera ikidodo hejuru y’amatwi yiwe no kumutima wiwe nuguca ishira ikiganza cayo kumaso yiwe, none ni nde azomu rongora munyuma y’Imana, mbega mwebwe ntimwibuka"
  45,24,"Nabo bavuze bati:- ntabuzima bwariho atari ubu buzima bwo ng’aha kw’Isi turapfa kandi nukubaho, kandi nta kiduhonya, atari ubu buzima bwo ng’aha kw’Isi, mugabo ntabumenyi bafise bw’ivyo bintu, mugabo naba kekeranya gusa"
  45,25,"No mugihe basomewe amajambo y’Imana matagatifu ari k’umugaragaro ntacitwazo bari bafise atari uko bavuga bati:- nimuzane abavyeyi banyu nimwaba mwebwe muvugisha ukuri kwama"
  45,26,"Vuga uti:- Imana niyo ibaha ubu buzima, hanyuma ikabica, hanyuma niyo izo begeranya mwese uko muri k’umusi w’imperuka ata makenga arimwo, mugabo abantu benshi ntavyo bazi"
  45,27,"N’ubwami bw’Amajuru n’Isi n’ubw’Imana, n’umusi hazoboneka umusi w’umuhero w’Isi uwo musi niho hazohonywa abazoba bashigikiranye n’amabi yose"
  45,28,"Uzobona imirwi y’abantu yose yapfukamye, n’umurwi umwe umwe uzohamagarwa uja gusoma igitabu cawo hanyuma ubwirwe uti:- uno musi uri hejuru nuwo guhembwa kuvyo mwahora mugira"
  45,29,"Iki gitabu cacu kibabwiza ukuri kwama, ntankeka rero twebwe twamye narindi twandika ivyo mwahora mugira vyose"
  45,30,"Nayo bamwe bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri bagatako bakagira ibikorwa vyiza ngaha kw’Isi, Umuremyi wabo azo binjiza mumigisha yayo, kuko niyo izoba ari intsinzi yabo iri k’umugaragaro"
  45,31,"Nayo abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri, bazobwirwa bati:- mbega ntamajambo yanje mwamye musomerwa namwe mugaca mwishima nukuba mu bantu babi cane"
  45,32,"Havuzwe hati:- mu vy’ukuri indagano y’Imana ni y’ukuri hamwe n’umusi w’imperuka ntamakenga arimwo, mwamye muvuga muti:- twebwe uwo musi w’umuhero w’Isi ntawo tuzi kandi twebwe ntaco twikeka atari uko ari ibihuha gusa kandi ntavyo twemera"
  45,33,"Rero amabi bakoze azogaragara, kandi azoba kikuza kuvyo bafashe minenerwe"
  45,34,"Hazovugwa hati:- uno musi turabibagiye nkuko namwe mwibagiye uyu musi wanyu, n’ivyicaro vyanyu nivyo mu muriro udahera, kandi ntawuzoba rokora"
  45,35,"Ivyo vyose n’ukubera yuko mwebwe mwafashe aya majambo y’Imana matagatifu minenerwe, hamwe n’ubuzima bwo ngaha kw’Isi nabwo buraba henda, rero uno musi uri hejuru ntawuzova muri uwo muriro udahera kandi ntibazo kwemererwa ivyitwazo vyabo"
  45,36,"Rero ihayagizwa ryose ryiza ni ry’Imana, umuremyi w’Amajuru, n’umuremyi w’Isi, n’umuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose"
  45,37,"N’ubukuru\tbwo\tmw’Ijuru\rno\rkw’Isi\rn’ubwiwe,\tkandi\tniyo\tnyene\rubushobozi n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  46,1,"Haa, Miiym. (Insiguro y’izi ndome hamwe n’uwufise ubumenyi bwazo zose n’Imana yonyene gusa)"
  46,2,"Imanurwa ryiki gitabu gitagatifu ca Qur’aani ryavuye ku Mana, nyene ubushobozi n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  46,3,"Ntitwaremye aya Majuru n’Isi canke ibiri hagati yavyo atari uko vyose ari ivy’ukuri, kandi ku kiringo categekanijwe, n’abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri barirengagiza kubutumwa batuzwa"
  46,4,"N’uvuge uti:- mbega mubona gute bamwe musenga, n’ukureka Imana y’ukuri, ni munyereke ico baremye ngaha kw’Isi, canke barafise ishirahamwe ry’ibiri mu majuru? Ni munzanire igitabu camyeho imbere yiki, canke ikimenyetso icarico cose c’ubumenyi, ni mwaba muvugisha ukuri"
  46,5,"N’abazimiye bakuru nibande gusumba bamwe basaba abatari Imana y’ukuri, nabo batazo bishura kugeza k’umusi w’imperuka, kandi batazi n’ibisabisho vy’abo"
  46,6,"Mugihe bazokwegeranywa abantu bazoba ari abansi b’abandi, kandi bazohakana amasengesho y’abo"
  46,7,"Mugihe bazosomerwa amajambo yacu matagatifu ari kumugaragaro, bamwe bahakana Imana yabo y’ukuri bazo vuga hejuru y’ukuri kuba shikira bati:- ubu n’uburozi buri k’umugaragaro"
  46,8,"Canke baka vuga bati:- niwe yavyi teguriye wenyene, vuga uti:- ni naba naravyi teguriye jewe, ntaco muzo mfasha imbere y’Imana, kuko niyo ifise ubumenyi bwivyo muriko muragira, kuko niyo ihagije kuba ariyo cabona hagati yanje na mwebwe, nayo niyo ifise ikigongwe n’impuhwe nyinshi zihagije"
  46,9,"Vuga uti:- jewe sindi igitangaro mu ntumwa z’Imana kandi nta bumenyi mfise bw’ingene nzogirwa, canke ingene muzogirwa mwebwe, ntakindi nkurikira atari ivyo neretswe kuri jewe, kandi nta nico narimwo atari ukuba ndi uwutuza gusa, kandi mbonekana k’umugaragaro"
  46,10,"Vuga uti:- mbega mubona gute iki gitabu nicaba kivuye ku Mana namwe mwagi hakanye n’ivyabona muri bene Israeri bari ivyabona k’uburorero bwibi, batako baremera ibi vyose, namwe mukagira amanyama, mu vy’ukuri Imana ntirongora abantu bahemukiye imitima yabo"
  46,11,"N’abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri barababwiye aba Isilamu bati:- iyo iba ari inzira y’amahoro, ntibari kudutanga mugihe batashoboye kurongoka kuri ibi, niho bavuze bati:- ubu n’ububeshi bw’abantu bakera"
  46,12,"N’imbere yiwe hari igitabu c’intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) kirongora kandi gifise impuhwe, niki n’igitabu cemeza kiri mururimi rw’icarabu, kugira ngo gituze bamwe bahemukiye imitima yabo, kandi kibe ikimenyetso c’abagira ineza"
  46,13,"Mu vy’ukuri bamwe bavuga bati:- Umuremyi wacu ni Mana, hanyuma bagatumbera inzira y’ukuri, abo ntabwoba bazoba bafise, kandi ntibazoteterwa"
  46,14,"Abo nibo bantu bo mw’Ijuru, bazobayo mu buzima bwabo bwose n’impembo yivyo bahora bagira"
  46,15,"Twarahanuye umuntu ngo agire ineza kubavyeyi biwe, kuko nyina wiwe yasamye imbanyi yiwe n’ingorane, n’ukumwibaruka muri izo ngorane nyene, n’ugusama kwiwe kugeza naho acuka kwafashe amezi mirongo itatu, kugeza naho ashika mubigero vyiwe n’ugushikana imyaka mirongo ine y’amavuko n’ukuvuga ati:- ewe Muremyi wanje, n’umfashe nshimire imigisha yawe wampaye hamwe n’abavyeyi banje, kandi umfashe kugira ibikorwa vyiza ukunda kandi ungarukire kubibondo vyanje, mu vy’ukuri jewe ndasavye ikigongwe kuri wewe, kandi mu vy’ukuri jewe ndi mubantu bemeye"
  46,16,"Abo nibo bantu twemerera ibikorwa vyabo vyiza bagize, hanyuma dugaca turengana iruhande y’ibikorwa vyabo bibi bakoze mubantu bo mw’ijuru kundagano z’ukuri bemerewe"
  46,17,"N’uwubwira abavyeyi biwe ijambo ry’akagayo, mukubatyoza n’ukubabwira yuko we azozurwa haciye ibinjana vyinshi imbere yabo, nabo bavyeyi babiri baguma basaba imfashanyo ku Mana, ahubwo ni wemere mu vy’ukuri indagano y’Imana ni y’ukuri, mugabo we yama yivugira ati:- ntivyari kuba ibi vyose mugabo n’ibigeragezo vyakorwa n’abantu baho hambere"
  46,18,"Abo nibo bantu intahe yategerezwa kuba kuribo hamwe n’ibihugu vyamyeho imbere yabo harimwo ibisigo n’abantu, mu vy’ukuri abo nibo bantu bitaye mu ruhombo"
  46,19,Bose bazoba bafise urugero rumwe kuvyo bakoze kugira ngo Imana ize ibarihe kubikorwa vyabo nabone ntibazo hemukirwa
  46,20,"N’umusi bazoshirwa abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri imbere y’umuriro udahera babwirwe bati:- mwara takaje ibintu vyanyu vyiza vyo mu buzima bwanyu bwo kw’Isi, mwebwe mwari nezereje kuri ivyo bintu, rero uno musi mura ronswa ibihano vy’ibimaramare kubera kurya kwishima kwanyu gusa ngaha kw’Isi, kandi kubera ukwiyonkora kwanyu"
  46,21,"N’ubibutse kuri mwene wabo Aadi mugihe yatuza abantu biwe bo mumigina y’imisenyi, mu vy’ukuri abatuza benshi muribo bavuye imbere yiwe n’inyuma yiwe ababwira ati:- ntimusenge uwariwe wese atari Imana yonyene gusa, mu vy’ukuri jewe ntinya kuri mwebwe ibihano vyuwo musi mukuru"
  46,22,"Nabo bishura bati:- uzanywe iwacu kugira ngo udutandukanishe n’Imana z’acu? Rero n’utuzanire ivyo watwemereye niwaba uri mubantu bavugisha ukuri"
  46,23,"Nawe abishura ati:- ubumenyi nyakuri buri ku Mana gusa, nanje ndabashikiriza kuvyo narungikanywe kurivyo, mugabo jewe ndababona y’uko mwebwe muri bantu bagira ibintu vy’ubujuju"
  46,24,"Rero mugihe babona igicu gitumbereye kumyaba yabo baciye bavuga bati:- iki n’igicu kituzaniye imvura, ahubwo nivyo mwahora mwipfuza yuko vyobashikira vuba na vuba, nawo n’umuyaga muriwo harimwo ibihano bibabaza cane"
  46,25,"Uwo muyaga n’uwuhonya ibintu vyose kw’itegeko ry’Umuremyi wayo, rero baba abata kiboneka burundu atari inzu zabo gusa, uku rero niko duhemba abantu babi"
  46,26,"Ntankeka twebwe twaraba tsimbataje muvyo twaba tsimbataje ko mwebwe, kuko twabahaye amatwi n’amaso n’imitima, mugabo amatwi yabo n’amaso yabo n’imitima yabo ntaco vyabamariye n’ikintu na kimwe mugihe bahakanye amajambo y’Imana matagatifu n’ugukikuzwa kuvyo bahora bafata minenerwe"
  46,27,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twarahoneje ibisagara vyaba kikuza kandi twaraba siguriye amajambo yacu matagatifu kugira ngo bikebuke ngo basubire muruhongore
  46,28,"None ko batafashijwe nizo Mana zabo bafashe n’ukureka Imana y’ukuri kugira ngo ibegereze kuriyo ahubwo yarabahubije, n’ubwo n’ububeshi bwabo bamye bategura"
  46,29,"Mugihe twakuzanira umurwi w’ibisigo vyaje kwumviriza amajambo y’Imana matagatifu ya Qur’ani, rero mugihe bashika baciye bongorerana bavuga bati:- ni muceceke, n’igihe hahezwa gusomwa ayo majambo baciye basubira kuncuti z’abo kubatuza"
  46,30,"Bavuze bati:- mwabantu bacu, mu vy’ukuri twebwe twumvise igitabu camanuwe munyuma y’intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) cemeza ivyabayeho imbere yiwe, kandi kikarongora abantu munzira y’ukuri, kandi kikarongora abantu munzira igororotse"
  46,31,"Mwa bantu bacu, ni mwitabire umushikiriza butumwa bw’Imana kandi mumwemere, namwe azobagirira ikigongwe ku bicumuro vyanyu, kandi azoba kingira n’ibihano bibabaza cane"
  46,32,"N’abatazo mwitaba uyo mushikiriza butumwa bw’Imana, abo bantu ntibazo nanira Imana kuri iy’Isi, kandi ntababa cungereye bafise imbere y’Imana, abo n’abantu bari mu buzimire bumwe buri k’umugaragaro"
  46,33,"Mbega ntibabona yuko Imana yaremye Amajuru n’Isi, kandi itarushe mu kuyarema, rero irafise ububasha bw’ukuzura aba shengeye? Egome mu vy’ukuri niyo nyene ububasha bw’ibintu vyose"
  46,34,"N’umusi bazojanwa aba bahakanyi b’Imana mu muriro udahera babwirwe bati:- none ibi vyose si ivy’ukuri? Nabo bazokwishura bati:- Egome! Kw’izina ry’Imana ni vy’ukuri, nayo ice ivuga iti:- ni muhonje ivyo bihano kubera ubuhakanyi bwanyu"
  46,35,"Rero niwigumye nk’uko bigumije za ntumwa z’Imana, zari zifise ubwihangane buniniya, kandi ntuba himirize kugahato, kuko k’umusi bazo kwibonera ivyo bemerewe bizoba nk’uko batabayeho ng’aha kw’Isi kubwabo ivyo bihano atari mumwanya w’isaha imwe gusa y’umurango, rero ubwo nibwo\tbutumwa\tbukwiye,\tkuko\thahonywa\tabatari\tabantu\tb’inkozi\tz’ibibi gusa"
  47,1,"Bamwe bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri n’ukuzitira inzira y’Imana y’ukuri, Imana niyo yonyene izo kwemeza ubugizi bubi bw’ibikorwa vyabo bagize"
  47,2,"Na bamwe bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri n’ukugira ibikorwa vyiza n’ukwemera ivya manuwe kuntumwa y’Imana Muhammadi (aui) kandi ari ivy’ukuri bivuye ku Muremyi wabo, abantu nkabo Imana izoba hanagurira ibicumuro vyabo kandi ibatsimbataze kubijanye n’ubuzima bwabo"
  47,3,"Ivyo vyose n’ukubera yuko bamwe bahakana Imana yabo y’ukuri bakurikiye ubuzimire, n’abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri naba kurikiye inzira y’ukuri ivuye ku Muremyi wabo, uko rero niko Imana ibagirira uburorero bw’ayo"
  47,4,"Rero muhuye na bamwe bahakana Imana y’ukuri, ni mubatere mumazosi yabo kugeza naho mubatsinda, aho niho muzoca muba bohera, kandi mubarekure kuneza canke bikombore bonyene kugeza naho intambara izocureha, nuko rero iyo Imana yihora kuribo mugabo kugira ngo Imana ibahe ibibazo bamwe muri mwebwe n’abandi na bamwe bicirwa munzira y’Imana, Imana ntizo kwiyibagiza ibikorwa vy’abo"
  47,5,Imana izoba yobora n’ukuba tsimbataza mu buzima bwabo
  47,6,Kandi izobinjiza mw’ijuru yaba menyesheje
  47,7,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, nimwa kingira idini ry’Imana, nayo izoba kingira bimwe biboneka kandi itsimbataze amaguru yanyu"
  47,8,"Nayo abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri, n’ibikorwa vyabo ntizo vyitaho"
  47,9,Ivyo vyose n’ukubera yuko bashavujwe n’ivyamanuwe n’Imana ica irasenyura ibikorwa vyabo
  47,10,Mbega ntiba kikuje kuri iy’Isi ngo birabire amaherezo y’ababaye ho imbere yabo? Imana yaraba honeje bose no kubahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri kuzoba nk’uko nyene
  47,11,"Ivyo vyose n’ukubera yuko Imana ariyo ikingira abayemeye bimwe bivuye k’umitima yabo, mugabo abahakanyi b’Imana yabo y’ukuri ntawuzoba kingira bafise"
  47,12,"Mu vy’ukuri Imana izo kwinjiza mw’ijuru abayemeye bimwe vy’ukuri n’ukugira ibikorwa vyiza, nabone izobinjiza mu mirima icamwo inzuzi imbere yabo, mugabo aba hakanye hamwe n’abi nezereza n’ugufungura nk’uko ibikoko bifungura no mumuriro udahera nibwo bwicaro bwabo"
  47,13,"N’ibisagara bingahe vyari bifise ubushobozi gusumba igisagara cawe wavuyemwo, abo bantu twarabahoneje bose kandi ntamufasha n’umwe bari bafise"
  47,14,"Mbega abantu bafise ivyemezo bivuye ku Muremyi wabo, boba bangana n’abantu basharijwe n’amabi y’ibikorwa vyabo bibi hamwe n’ugukurikira ivyo imitima yabo yipfuza gusa"
  47,15,"Akarorero k’Ijuru bemerewe abantu beranda nuko muri ayo majuru harimwo inzuzi z’amazi atavunda n’inzuzi z’amata atononekara kukanovera kayo hamwe n’inzuzi z’inzoga ziboreza zifise akanovera kuba zinywa hamwe n’inzuzi z’ubuki zisukuye neza, no muri ayo majuru bazoronswa mwo ivyamwa vy’ubwoko bwose hamwe n’imbabazi zivuye ku Muremyi wabo, rero abo bantu bazoba bangana na barya bicaye mumuriro udahera n’ukunyweshwa amazi y’amarike azocagagura amara yabo"
  47,16,"Hari n’abandi muribo bakwumviriza kugeza naho baganuka bavuye iwawe, bagaca babaza bamwe bahawe ubumenyi bati:- mbega ubu yavuze iki? Abo bantu nibo Imana yateyeko ikidodo kumitima yabo n’ugukurikira ivyo imitima yabo yipfuza"
  47,17,Na bamwe bemeye kurongoka Imana ibongereza ukurongoka kwabo n’ukubaha ubugamburutsi bwabo bw’Imana
  47,18,"Mbega barindiriye ikindi kintu nyabaki atari umusi w’umuhero w’Isi uzoba shikira giturumbuka, nayo ibimenyetso vyawo biramaze gushika, none ukwibuka kwabo kuzoba fasha iki mugihe bazo shikirwa n’uwo musi"
  47,19,"Umenye yuko atawundi asengwa bimwe vy’ukuri atari Imana yonyene gusa, kandi usabe ikigongwe kubijanye n’ibicumuro vyawe hamwe n’ibicumuro vyaba Isilamu b’abagabo hamwe n’aba Isilamu kazi, n’Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi bwaho muzoja n’ukugaruka hamwe naho muzoba"
  47,20,"N’abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri bavuga bati:- ni kuki hata manurwa igisomwa, mugabo mugihe hamanuwe igisomwa nyaco no murico havurwa mwo inkuru z’ingwano, uca ubona bamwe bafise indwara mu mitima yabo bakwitegereza nkabaguye igihumure c’urupfu noneho ntakundi bari kugira"
  47,21,"Ubugamburutsi hamwe n’imvugo nziza hamwe n’ijambo rigomba kuja mungiro nirishirwe mungiro niba ari abanyakuri ku Mana, ntankeka bizoba ari vyiza cane kuribo"
  47,22,Nivyo bizeye kuri mwebwe mukuba abononyi ngaha kw’Isi n’ukwanka imiryango yanyu mugihe mwaronse ubutegetsi
  47,23,"Abo nibo bantu Imana yavumye, nukuba shirako ubutumva kumatwi y’abo n’ukuba humya amaso yabo"
  47,24,"Mbega ntibategera neza iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu, canke mu mitima y’abo irugarijwe mwo amagufuri"
  47,25,"Mu vy’ukuri bamwe basubira inyuma n’imigongo yabo mugihe bamaze kuboneshwa uburokoke, bamenye yuko Shetani yabahenze, n’Imana iracabaha umwanya"
  47,26,"Ivyo n’ukubera yuko babwiwe bamwe bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri bashavuye kuvyo Imana yamanuye bavuga yuko twebwe tuzoba gamburukira muri bimwe mubintu, n’Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’amabanga yabo"
  47,27,None bizoba gute mugihe Abamarayika bazobica n’ukuba kubita mumaso yabo no kumigongo yabo
  47,28,"Ivyo vyose n’ukubera yuko bakurikiye ivya shavujije Imana nabo bashavuzwa n’ibinezereza Imana, n’ukubikurira imigisha y’ibikorwa vyabo"
  47,29,Mbega bamwe bafise indwara mumitima yabo biyumvira yuko Imana itazo serura amabi yabo
  47,30,"Iyo dushaka twari kukwereka n’ukubamenya kubimenyetso vyabo, mugabo urashobora kubamenya kumvugo zabo, n’Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ibikorwa vyanyu"
  47,31,"Tuzoba girira ibibazo kugeza naho tuzo bereka bamwe barwanira idini muri mwebwe hamwe n’abihangana, natwe tuzoserura inkuru zanyu"
  47,32,"Mu vy’ukuri bamwe bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri n’ukuzitirira abantu inzira y’Imana y’ukuri n’ukurwanya intumwa y’Imana mu nyuma yaho imaze kubereka uburokoke, kuri bo ntakibi nakimwe bazogirira Imana, kandi ibintu vyabo izobisenyura n’ibikorwa vy’abo bagize"
  47,33,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri nimu gamburukire Imana yanyu y’ukuri kandi mugamburukire intumwa y’Imana, kandi ntimwonone ibikorwa vyanyu mwagize"
  47,34,"Mu vy’ukuri bamwe bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri hamwe n’ukuzitira inzira y’Imana, hanyuma bakitaba Umuremyi wabo nabo ari abahakanyi b’Imana, Imana ntizobagirira ikigongwe"
  47,35,"Rero ntimudebukirwe nukuta giriranira umwumvikano hagati yanyu, kuko mwebwe nimwe muzoronka intsinzi, n’Imana iri kumwe namwe, kuko ntizobima imigisha y’ibikorwa vyanyu"
  47,36,"Mu vy’ukuri ubuzima bw’Isi n’urufyino kandi ntaco bumaze, kandi nimwemera n’ukwikingira n’amabi yose, Imana izobaha impembo yanyu, kandi ntizoba saba amatungo yanyu mufise"
  47,37,"Niyaba saba ivyo vyose n’ukuba fatira kumatungo yanyu muzoca muba ingumyi, n’Imana izoca ibakurira izo ngorane zanyu mufise"
  47,38,"Mbega ni mwebwe muhamagarirwa ngo mutange amatungo yanyu munzira y’Imana, hakaba hari n’abandi muri mwebwe bigira ingumyi, rero uwigira ingumyi amenye neza yuko abigirira umutima wiwe wenyene, n’Imana niyo nyene amatungo yose, namwe nimwe muri abahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri, rero nimwa subira inyuma mumenye yuko Imana izosubizaho abandi bantu atari mwebwe kandi ntibazoba nkamwe"
  48,1,Mu vy’ukuri twaraguhaye intsinzi iri k’umugaragaro
  48,2,Kugira ngo Imana ikugirire ikigongwe kubicumuro vyawe vy’abaye hamwe n’ibizoza hamwe n’ukugukwiriza imigisha yayo n’ukukurongora munzira igororotse
  48,3,Kandi Imana igukingire n’ikingiro ry’inguvu nyinshi cane
  48,4,"Niyo yamanuye ihumure mumitima yaba Isilamu kugira ngo bongereze ukwemera hejuru y’ukwemera kwabo, n’ingabo zo mw’Ijuru no kw’Isi ni z’Imana, nayo niyo ifise ubumenyi n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  48,5,"Kugira ngo winjize aba Isilamu b’abagabo hamwe n’aba Isilamu kazi mumirima icamwo inzuzi imbere yabo n’ukubayo mu buzima bwabo bwose hamwe n’ukuba hanagurira ibicumuro vyabo vyose, iyi rero niyo ntsinzi niniya imbere y’Imana"
  48,6,"Hanyuma ihane ababeshi b’abagabo n’ababeshi b’abakenyezi hamwe n’abagereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu b’abagabo hamwe n’abagereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu b’abakenyezi n’abikeka ku Mana imyikeko mibi abo bantu bazo shikirwa n’ihindagurika ribi cane, n’Imana ize ibashavurire n’ukuba vuma n’ukuba tegurira umuriro witiriwe Jahannamu, nayo n’ingaruka mbi cane"
  48,7,"N’ingabo zo mw’Ijuru no kw’Isi ni z’Imana, nayo niyo nyene ubushobozi n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  48,8,Mu vy’ukuri twakuzanye wewe ngo ube icabona n’umushikiriza butumwa bwiza hamwe n’ugutuza
  48,9,Kugira ngo mwemere Imana yanyu y’ukuri hamwe n’intumwa y’iwe kandi muyihayagize kandi muyisonere n’ukuyi hayagiza kuva mu gitondo no k’umugoroba
  48,10,"Ntankeka abo mucuditse nabo hamwe, mu vy’ukuri bacuditse hamwe n’Imana, kuko ukuboko kw’Imana kuri hejuru y’amaboko yabo, rero uwuzota amasezerano yayo azoba ataye amasezerano y’umutima wiwe, nayo uwuzoyafata nka nkama nk’uko Imana yaya mwemereye Imana izo muhemba impembo niniya cane"
  48,11,"Bazo kubwira b’abanyagihugu bicaye inyuma y’abandi bati:- amatungo yacu hamwe n’abacu nibo badu koresheje, rero n’udusabire imbabazi kuko bavugisha indimi zabo kubitari mu mitima yabo, na wewe n’uvuge uti:- ni nde ashoboye kuba fasha kukintu icarico cose ku Mana niyaba ishaka kuba girira inabi canke ishatse kuba girira ineza? Rero ahubwo Imana niyo ifise inkuru y’ivyo mugira vyose"
  48,12,"Mugabo mwiketse yuko intumwa y’Imana hamwe naba Isilamu batazo garuka burundu ku bantu babo n’ugusharizwa n’ivyo mu mitima yanyu, kandi mwiketse imyikeko mibi, namwe mwamaze kuba muri mu bantu bazo honywa"
  48,13,"N’abatemera Imana yabo y’ukuri hamwe n’intumwa yayo, mu vy’ukuri twaraba teguriye abo bahakanyi b’Imana umuriro ukaze cane"
  48,14,"N’ubwami bw’Amajuru n’Isi nubw’Imana kuko niyo igira ikigongwe kuwo yishakiye n’uguhana kuwo yishakiye, ni nayo ifise imbabazi n’ikigongwe cinshi gihagije"
  48,15,"Bazovuga bamwe bicara inyuma y’abandi mugihe bazo genda gutora amatungo yo mungwano niho bazoca bavuga bati:- ni mutureke tujane namwe kuko bagomba guhindura amajambo y’Imana matagatifu, wewe n’uvuge uti:- mwebwe ntimu dukurikire kuko Imana iramaze kuvumera kuva kera y’uko, bazovuga yuko:- mwebwe mura twinuba, nabo ntavyo bari bazi atari ibintu bikeyi gusa"
  48,16,"Babwire bamwe basigara inyuma muri babantu bo mubugararwa yuko ubu vuba muzo hamagarwa kugenda mungwano n’abantu bafise ubumenyi bukaze bw’ingwano, kuko muzo rwana nabo canke bazoneshwa, rero nimwa gamburukira Imana izobaha impembo yanyu nziza, rero nimwa hindukira nkuko mwahindukiye aho hambere Imana izoba hana ibihano bibabaza cane"
  48,17,"Impumyi iyariyo yose ntamwikomo igirirwa, canke ikimuga na cone ntamwikomo kigirirwa, hamwe n’umurwayi niko kuko nyene, n’uwu gamburukira Imana hamwe n’intumwa yiwe izo mwinjiza mu mirima icamwo inzuzi imbere yiwe, n’uwuzo hindukira iruhande, Imana izomuhana ibihano bibabaza cane"
  48,18,"Mu vy’ukuri Imana yarabagiriye imbabazi aba Isilamu mugihe bagira urunani hamwe na wewe muri munsi y’igiti, kandi Imana yari ifise ubumenyi bw’ibiri mumitima yanyu, hanyuma ica iramanura ihumure kuribo, n’ukubaha intsinzi y’igihe kigufiya cane"
  48,19,"N’ivyo muzo ronkera mu ngwano ari vyinshi no mubazo zironka, n’Imana niyo ifise ubushobozi n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  48,20,"Imana yarabemereye muvyo muzo ronkera mungwano ari nyinshi, hanyuma ibazanira ibi vyose ubwambere hanyuma ica irakingira amaboko y’abantu ntaba shikire kugira ngo kibabere ikimenyetso kuba Isilamu n’ukuba rongora mu nzira igororotse"
  48,21,"N’ibindi mutashoboye kuronkera mundwano, Imana yaramaze kubikikuza, nayo niyo nyene ubushobozi bw’ibintu vyose"
  48,22,"Iyo abo bahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri batana mu mitwe namwe ntankeka bari kubaha imigongo, hanyuma ntibari kuronka uwuba cungera canke uwuba fasha"
  48,23,"Ibi n’ibisanzwe ku Mana kuvyabaye aho hambere, kandi ntuzo ronka ihindagurika ry’ibintu bisanzwe vy’Imana"
  48,24,"N’Imana niyo yazitiye amaboko yabo kuri mwebwe, hamwe n’amaboko yanyu kuribo, muri mumwaba w’igisagara c’iMakkat, imaze kubaha intsinzi kuribo, n’Imana irabona ivyo mugira vyose"
  48,25,"Abo nibo bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri n’ukuba kingira kutaja mungoro y’Imana ntagatifu, batako baba zitirira kuri zantungwa zanyu ntizishike aho zagenewe gushika, rero iyo hataba abagabo baba isilamu hamwe naba Isilamu kazi ata bumenyi bafise kugira ngo ntimuba honyange namwe mutabazi no kuri ivyo vyose mugaca mufatwa n’umubabaro kuribo kugira ngo Imana yinjize mw’ijuru uwo yishakiye mubwami bwayo, rero iyo bacanamwo ntankeka twari kubahana bamwe bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri muribo hamwe n’ibihano bibabaza cane"
  48,26,"Hamwe barya bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri, mugihe bashira mumitima yabo ingoga z’ubujuju, aho niho Imana yamanura ihumure kuntumwa yiwe no hejuru yaba Isilamu, n’ukuba tegeka ijambo ry’ubugamburutsi, nabo bari bene ukuri gusumba ababikwiye, n’Imana niyo nyene ubumenyi bw’ibintu vyose"
  48,27,"Mu vy’ukuri Imana yaremereye intumwa yiwe indoto yiwe y’ukuri, yuko atankeka ko muzo kwinjira mw’isengero ritagatifu Imana ibishatse mu mahoro meza mwimosheje imitwe yanyu, canke mwagabanije, aho ntabwoba muzoba mufise n’Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ivyo mutazi, rero imbere y’ibi vyose izobaha intsinzi iri hafi cane"
  48,28,"Imana niyo yarungitse intumwa yiwe kuba ariyo ndongozi n’idini ry’ukuri, kugira ngo intsinzi ibe hejuru y’amadini yose, n’Imana irahagije kuba iriyo cabona"
  48,29,"Intumwa y’Imana Muhammadi (aui) niyo ntumwa y’Imana hamwe n’abari kumwe nayo n’abafise imitima rugabo imbere y’abahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri, naba giriranira ikigongwe bamwe n’abandi, rero uzoba bona bunamye n’ugushira imitwe yabo hasi barondera imigisha y’Imana n’impuhwe zayo, ibimenyetso bibaranga nibi boneka kumaso yabo kubera ukwunamika imitwe yabo hasi, ubwo nibwo burorero buri mu gitabu gitagatifu ca Taurati n’akandi karorero ni mugitabu c’Injili, nkuko igiterwa casohoye amashami yaco n’ukugiha inguvu kika vyibuha kigahagarara neza hejuru y’igishitsi c’ayo n’ukunezereza abagiteye kugira ngo gishavuze abahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri kurico, n’Imana yarabemereye abayemeye bimwe bivuye k’umutima n’ukugira ibikorwa vyiza muribo hamwe n’ikigongwe n’impembo niniya cane"
  49,1,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana y’ukuri, ntimu tanguze kuvuga imbere y’Imana ijambo n’imbere y’intumwa yiwe, kandi mutinye Imana yanyu y’ukuri mu vy’ukuri niyo yumva kandi niyo nyene ubumenyi buhagije"
  49,2,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri ntimuduze amajwi yanyu gusumba ijwi ry’intumwa y’Imana kandi ntimu muvugishe kw’ijwi ry’inguvu nk’uko muvugana bamwe n’abandi, ntihaze haboneke ibikorwa vyanyu bibura imigisha namwe mutabizi"
  49,3,"Mu vy’ukuri bamwe bacisha bugufi amajwi yabo imbere y’intumwa y’Imana, abo nibo Imana yasukuye imitima yabo mugutinya Imana yabo, rero kuribo hazoba ikigongwe hamwe n’imihezagiro mininiya cane"
  49,4,"Bamwe baguhamagarira inyuma y’impome z’ivyumba, benshi muribo ntana kimwe bazi"
  49,5,"Iyo batenyenya kugeza aho uzoba seruka ko vyari kuba vyiza kuribo, n’Imana niyo nyene ikigongwe n’impuhwe zihagije"
  49,6,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, nimwa shikirwa n’umwangushi afise inkuru iyariyo yose nimu yitohoze neza, kugira ngo ntimuze mute abantu mukaga kubera ubujuju bwanyu, hanyuma ntimuze mwihebure kubintu mwagize"
  49,7,"Mumenye yuko intumwa y’Imana iri kumwe namwe, iyo iba gamburukira mubintu vyinshi, ntankeka mwari kugira ingorane mugabo Imana yaraba shajije kubu Isilamu bwanyu nuku bushariza mu mitima yanyu, nayo niyo yabagiriye urwanko rw’uguhakana ubuhakanyi bw’Imana n’ukwidohora mu nzira y’ukuri, abo nibo bantu barongotse"
  49,8,Kubera imihezagiro y’Imana n’imigisha yayo nuko Imana ifise ubumenyi n’ubuhizi buhagije
  49,9,"Ni haba imirwi ibiri muba Isilamu iriko irarwana, rero nimuje hagati yayo muyibanguranye, nihaba umwe muri uwo murwi uhemukiye uwundi, ni muwurwanye uwo murwi ubonera uwundi kugeza aho usubira kumategeko y’Imana, niwa subira ni muwuhuze hagati yawo mukoresheje ubutungane bw’ukuri, rero mubacire urubanza rw’ukuri mu vy’ukuri Imana ikunda abaca imanza z’ukuri"
  49,10,"Mu vy’ukuri aba Isilamu bose n’abavukanyi, rero ni muhuze abari hagati y’abavukanyi banyu, kandi mutinye Imana yanyu kugira ngo muronke impuhwe zayo"
  49,11,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, abagabo ntiba kengere abagabo bagenzi babo, nkumbure wosanga ari abantu ngira kamaro kubasumba, n’abapfasoni ntiba bakengere abapfasoni bagenzi babo, nkumbure wosanga aribo bantu ngira kamaro kubasumba, kandi ntimutukane mu koresheje amoko yanyu, kandi ntimuhamagarane kumazina mabi y’akagayo, rero izina ribi ryo birwa umuntu ngo yiyonkoye mw’idini rya Isilamu nawe ari umu Isilamu, rero abadasaba ikigongwe abo nibo bahemukiye imitima yabo"
  49,12,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, ni mwirinde cane n’ukwikekana, kuko ukwikekana n’igicumuro, kandi ntimusume insaku, kandi muri mwebwe nti mwongorerane n’abandi, mbega umwe muri mwebwe yonezerwa afunguye inyama ya mwene wabo yapfuye? Oya! ntivyoba nezereza, rero nimutinye Imana yanyu ntankeka Imana niyo yakira ikigongwe n’impuhwe zihagije"
  49,13,"Mwebwe bantu, mu vy’ukuri twarabaremye tubakuye k’umugabo n’umugore n’ukubagira amakungu n’amoko kugira ngo mumenyane gusa, mu vy’ukuri uwusonerwa cane muri mwebwe imbere y’Imana n’urya agamburukira Imana yiwe cane, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi n’inkuru z’ibintu vyose"
  49,14,"Baravuze ababa m’ubugararwa bati:- twebwe turemeye, nawe n’ubishure uti:- mwebwe ntimuremera mugabo ni muvuge muti:- twebwe turagamburutse n’ukwemera kwanyu, mugabo uko kwemera kwanyu ntikurinjira neza mu mitima yanyu, nimwa gamburukira Imana yanyu hamwe n’intumwa yayo, Imana ntizoba gabaniriza icarico cose mubikorwa vyanyu, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo ifise ikigongwe cinshi, kandi niyo ifise impuhwe zihagije"
  49,15,"Abemera Imana yabo bimwe bivuye k’umutima yabo nibarya bayemeye hamwe n’intumwa yayo, hanyuma bakaba badafise amakenga mukurwanira Idini ry’Imana bakoresheje amatungo yabo n’imitima yabo, abo bantu nibo bameye bimwe vy’ukuri"
  49,16,"Vuga uti:- mwebwe mumenyesha idini ry’Imana ry’ububeshi, mugihe Imana ifise ubumenyi bw’ibiri mu Majuru no kw’Isi, kandi ariyo nyene ubumenyi bw’ibintu vyose"
  49,17,"Barakugora mu kwinjira kw’abo mw’idini rya Isilamu, wewe vuga uti:- nti mubigire yuko ari ineza kuri jewe mukuba kwanyu aba Isilamu, ahubwo Imana niyo y’abagiriye iyo neza mu kubarongora mw’idini rya Isilamu ni mwaba muri abanyakuri"
  49,18,"Ntankeka Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ibintu vyinyegeje biri mu Majuru no kw’Isi, nayo niyo ibona ivyo mugira vyose"